ession-build-empire-2020-11%5C%22%3Edelight%20customers%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20without%20sitting%20in%20an%20office%20in%20Seattle%2C%20why%20should%20I%20be%20expected%20to%20move%3F%20Even%20before%20the%20pandemic%2C%20I%20wasn't%20going%20in%20three%20days%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20crappy%20time%20to%20be%20looking%20for%20a%20new%20job%20as%20a%20developer.%20The%20jobs%20I'm%20looking%20at%20are%20significant%20pay%20cuts.%20Companies%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flayoffs-sweeping-the-us-these-are-the-companies-making-cuts-2023%5C%22%3Elaying%20off%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20forcing%20the%20rest%20to%20relocate%2C%20which%20is%20driving%20more%20people%20out%20of%20work.%20It%20leads%20to%20frustrating%20and%20worrisome%20discussions%20with%20hiring%20managers%20where%20I%20have%20to%20ask%2C%20%26quot%3BOkay%2C%20it's%20remote%20today.%20Will%20it%20be%20remote%20tomorrow%3F%26quot%3B%20No%20one%20is%20giving%20a%20certain%20answer.%20I%20have%20a%20hard%20time%20trusting%20they%20won't%20roll%20it%20back%20someday%20because%20that's%20what's%20happening%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20were%20to%20take%20a%20new%20remote%20job%20somewhere%2C%20all%20it%20might%20take%20is%20one%20senior%20manager%20or%20C-level%20person%20to%20get%20replaced%2C%20and%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%20everyone%20has%20to%20be%20back%20in%20office.%20As%20someone%20who%20is%20straight%20up%20unwilling%20to%20move%2C%20that%20means%20I%20could%20just%20lose%20my%20job%20for%20reasons%20entirely%20unrelated%20to%20my%20performance%20at%20any%20moment%20at%20any%20company%2C%20and%20that's%20scary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20see%20myself%20ever%20coming%20back%20here.%20Too%20many%20bridges%20have%20been%20burned.%20I'm%20just%20done%20with%20it.%20I'm%20at%20the%20point%20now%20where%20if%20Amazon%20said%2C%20we'll%20take%20everything%20back%20and%20you%20can%20have%20your%20job%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20accept%20it.%20I%20don't%20trust%20anyone%20there%20enough%20at%20this%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20Amazon%20spokesperson%20Brad%20Glasser%20sent%20the%20following%20statement%20to%20Insider%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Csection%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BInsider%20wouldn't%20provide%20the%20information%20necessary%20for%20us%20to%20verify%20this%20individual's%20account%2C%20but%20if%20it's%20true%2C%20it%20doesn't%20reflect%20the%20experience%20of%20most%20employees.%20We%20believe%20that%20being%20in%20the%20office%20at%20least%20three%20days%20a%20week%20is%20the%20right%20long-term%20approach%20because%20it%C2%A0drives%20culture%2C%20team%20connection%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20learning.%20While%20we%20understand%20that%20some%20people%20might%20not%20agree%20with%20our%20approach%2C%20we've%20consistently%20explained%20that%20it%20would%20evolve%20since%20we%20started%20to%20emerge%20from%20the%20pandemic%20and%20began%20experimenting%20with%20how%20our%20teams%20worked.%C2%A0As%20part%20of%20this%20process%2C%20we're%20asking%C2%A0a%20relatively%20small%20percentage%20of%20our%20team%20to%20relocate%2C%20and%20we're%20communicating%20directly%20with%20those%20affected%20and%20providing%20relocation%20support.%C2%A0Now%20that%20we%20have%20a%20few%20months%20under%20our%20belts%20with%20more%20people%20in%20the%20office%20more%20frequently%2C%20there's%20more%20energy%2C%20connection%2C%20and%20collaboration%2C%20and%20we're%20hearing%20that%20from%20employees%20and%20the%20businesses%20that%20surround%20our%20offices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20an%20employee%2C%20at%20Amazon%20or%20elsewhere%2C%20with%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20how%20return-to-office%20plans%20have%20affected%20you%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20from%20a%20non-work%20device%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Asjackson%40insider.com%5C%22%20ta