h%20ceilings%2C%20or%20that%20kind%20of%20interesting%20structural%20system%2C%20or%20that%20kind%20of%20heritage%20facade%2C%20or%20building%20with%20brick%20skin%2C%26quot%3B%20Paynter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20renovated%20exterior%20of%20Franklin%20Tower%2C%20a%2024-story%20former%20office%20building%20in%20downtown%20Philadelphia%20that%20now%20contains%20luxury%20residences.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef8c0d6f301e00193e61b2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20renovated%20exterior%20of%20Franklin%20Tower%2C%20a%2024-story%20former%20office%20building%20in%20downtown%20Philadelphia%20that%20now%20contains%20luxury%20residences.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gensler%20and%20Robert%20Deitchler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20even%20in%20a%20worst-case%20scenario%2C%20where%20units%20are%20strangely%20laid%20out%20or%20dimly%20lit%2C%20there%20can%20still%20be%20unique%20benefits%20to%20living%20in%20an%20old%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20might%20not%20care%20that%20they%20get%20a%20ton%20of%20daylight%20into%20their%20bedroom%20if%20it%20means%20their%20rent%20is%20cheaper%20or%20they%20live%20a%20five-minute%20walk%20from%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20Mark%20Hogan%2C%20a%20San%20Francisco%20architect%20who%20has%20advised%20the%20city%20government%20on%20policy%20reforms%20concerning%20office%20conversions%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20renovating%20old%20office%20buildings%20is%20no%20simple%20task.%20Insider%20spoke%20with%20four%20architects%20who'd%20tackled%20these%20projects.%20They%20said%20that%20turning%20a%20cubicle%20farm%20or%20conference%20room%20into%20a%20livable%20space%20involved%20addressing%20a%20host%20of%20issues%2C%20including%20inoperable%2C%20poorly%20insulated%20windows%20and%20the%20dark%20depths%20of%20a%20skyscraper's%20center.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20it%20takes%20to%20turn%20an%20empty%20office%20skyscraper%20into%20much-needed%20housing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20first%20step%20is%20finding%20the%20right%20building%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20difficult%20part%20of%20the%20conversion%20process%20comes%20before%20any%20of%20the%20construction%20begins%3A%20selecting%20the%20buildings%20to%20convert%2C%20Paynter%20said.%20He%20and%20his%20team%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconvert-vacant-offices-to-apartments-gensler-steven-paynter-2023-1%5C%22%3Edeveloped%20an%20algorithm%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20determine%20which%20buildings%20are%20ripe%20for%20conversion.%20It%20takes%20into%20account%20building%20size%2C%20layout%2C%20location%2C%20and%20how%20updated%20its%20facade%20is.%20Of%20the%20950%20buildings%20he%20and%20his%20team%20have%20surveyed%2C%20just%2030%25%20are%20suitable%20for%20conversion.%20People%20in%20the%20industry%20call%20them%20%26quot%3BGoldilocks%20buildings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20get%20the%20right%20building%2C%20you%20can%20make%20a%20really%20great%20project%20out%20of%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20start%20with%20the%20wrong%20building%2C%20you've%20got%20no%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOlder%2C%20prewar%20buildings%20are%20generally%20easier%20to%20turn%20into%20homes%20than%20newer%20skyscrapers.%20That's%20because%20buildings%20constructed%20before%20air%20conditioning%20generally%20have%20smaller%20floor%20plates%2C%20with%20building%20interiors%20no%20more%20than%2025%20or%2030%20feet%20from%20windows%20that%20can%20open.%20Newer%20buildings%20often%20have%20deeper%20floor%20plates%20and%20windows%20that%20don't%20open%2C%20which%20can%20make%20conversion%20tricky%20since%20residential%20buildings%20need%20light%2C%20air%2C%20and%20bathrooms%20all%20over.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20older%20buildings%20that%20are%20U-shaped%20or%20E-shaped%2C%20or%20kind%20of%20smaller%20in%20floor%20plate%20are%20perfect%20candidates%20for%20conversion%2C%26quot%3B%20Charles%20Bloszies%2C%20a%20San%20Francisco%20architect%20and%20structural%20engineer%2C%20told%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20particularly%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20postwar%20high-rises%2C%20it's%20more%20economical%20to%20tear%20old%20office%20buildings%20down%20and%20replace%20them%20with%20new%20housing%2C%20Hogan%20said.%20He%20thinks%20older%2C%20smaller%20buildings%20are%20much%20more%20eligible%20for%20conversion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20lower-hanging%20fruit%2C%20and%20I%20think%20those%20are%20the%20type%20of%20projects%20you'll%20be%20more%20likely%20to%20see%20sooner%2C%26quot%3B%20Hogan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20exercise%20and%20lounge%20space%20and%20roof%20deck%20in%20Franklin%20Tower%2C%20a%20former%20office%20building%20in%20downtown%20Philadelphia.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ef8b266f301e00193e603c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20exercise%20and%20lounge%20space%20in%20Franklin%20Tower.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Gensler%20and%20Robert%20Deitchler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EMany%20buildings%20need%20more%20stairs%20to%20meet%20modern%20fire%20codes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20in%20turning%20a%20commercial%20building%20into%20homes%20is%20figuring%20out%20where%20the%20staircases%20will%20go%20to%20meet%20modern%20fire%20regulations%2C%20especially%20in%20older%20and%20smaller%20buildings%2C%20Hogan%20said.%20In%20the%20US%2C%20most%20apartment%20buildings%20more%20than%204%20stories%20high%20must%20have%20two%20staircases%20and%20exits.%20Those%20staircases%20need%20to%20be%20connected%20by%20a%20corridor%2C%20and%20that%20shapes%20how%20apartments%20are%20laid%20out%20around%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20existing%20buildings%20that%20have%20a%20fire%20escape%20as%20a%20second%20means%20of%20egress%20in%20San%20Francisco%2C%26quot%3B%20Hogan%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20a%20building%20where%20you're%20changing%20the%20use%2C%20you%20typically%20have%20to%20bring%20it%20up%20to%20code%2C%20and%20so%20adding%20extra%20stairs%20is%20a%20really%20major%20intervention%20and%20is%20just%20going%20to%20change%20the%20available%20square%20footage%20pretty%20dramatically.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECutting%20out%20the%20middle%20of%20skyscrapers%20to%20add%20more%20windows%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKey%20to%20the%20interior%20design%20in%20converted%20buildings%20is%20maximizing%20the%20amount%20of%20exterior%20wall%20per%20unit%20to%20get%20each%20home%20the%20most%20light%20and%20air%20possible.%20In%20some%20newer%20office%20buildings%2C%20architects%20will%20cut%20out%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20center%20of%20the%20building%20to%20create%20a%20courtyard%20or%20shaft%20for%20air%20and%20light.%20Sometimes%20that%20lost%20floor%20space%20will%20be%20made%20up%20by%20adding%20several%20floors%20to%20the%20building.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Cetra%2C%20a%20Manhattan%20architect%20who%20has%20worked%20on%20office%20conversions%20since%20the%201980s%2C%20is%20leading%20the%20second-largest%20office-to-residential%20conversion%20project%20in%20Manhattan.%20The%20building%20%E2%80%94%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewyorkyimby.com%2F2022%2F12%2Fdevelopers-close-on-535m-loan-to-redevelop-25-water-street-in-financial-district-manhattan.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E25%20Water%20St.%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20financial%20district%20%E2%80%94%20houses%20JPMorgan's%20offices%20and%20is%20set%20to%20have%201%2C300%20apartments%20eventually.%20But%20first%2C%20sections%20of%20the%20center%20of%20the%20building%2C%20including%20excess%20elevators%2C%20are%20planned%20to%20be%20cut%20out%2C%20with%20new%20floors%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20created%20the%20hole%20in%20the%20doughnut%20to%20bring%20the%20light%20and%20air%20into%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Cetra%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20we%20took%20some%20of%20the%20floor%20area%20that%20we%20eliminated%2C%20and%20we're%20building%2010%20stories%20on%20top%20of%20the%20building.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20co-working%20space%20at%2055%20Broad%20Street%20in%20Manhattan.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64e75873a7adf7001906e51c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20a%20coworking%20space%20at%2055%20Broad%20St%20in%20Manhattan.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20CetraRuddy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20such%20project%20completed%20in%202007%2C%20Bloszies%20and%20his%20team%20turned%20the%20oldest%20skyscraper%20on%20the%20West%20Coast%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelisamovement.com%2Freborn%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DFinished%2520in%25201890%252C%2520the%2520Chronicle%2Coffice%2520building%2520converted%2520to%2520residential.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESan%20Francisco's%20Chronicle%20Building%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20into%20100%20homes.%20They%20stripped%20off%20a%20metal%20shroud%20that%20had%20been%20added%20to%20the%20building%2C%20restored%20the%20original%20facade%2C%20and%20added%208%20stories%20to%20the%20top%20of%20the%20building%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20vertical%20additions%20to%20a%20historic%20building%20in%20the%20world%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ERebuilding%20a%20skyscraper%20can%20get%20expensive%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20all%20buildings%20can%20accommodate%20a%20renovation%20like%20this.%20Some%20building%20foundations%20can't%20handle%20the%20extra%20weight%20of%20additional%20floors.%20Cetra%20said%20he%20and%20his%20team%20%26quot%3Bdraw%20the%20line%26quot%3B%20at%20reinforcing%20foundations%2C%20a%20process%20that%20he%20said%20was%20too%20expensive%20and%20disruptive%20to%20be%20worthwhile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChanging%20an%20older%20building's%20use%20often%20triggers%20requirements%20to%20have%20it%20abide%20by%20modern%20building%20codes.%20This%20includes%20updates%20like%20seismic%20retrofitting%2C%20which%20strengthens%20buildings%20to%20protect%20them%20against%20earthquakes.%20It%20also%20includes%20abiding%20by%20modern%20energy-efficiency%20standards.%20New%20plumbing%2C%20mechanical%20systems%2C%20and%20heating%2C%20ventilation%2C%20and%20air-conditioning%20systems%20are%20also%20usually%20part%20of%20the%20construction%20process.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERenovating%20the%20facades%20and%20windows%20of%20buildings%20is%20also%20a%20costly%20but%20often%20necessary%20endeavor.%20Many%20buildings%2C%20particularly%20those%20constructed%20after%201960%2C%20don't%20have%20operable%20windows%2C%20and%20even%20if%20they%20do%2C%20they%20don't%20meet%20modern%20energy-efficiency%20standards.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gensler%20renovated%20Franklin%20Tower%2C%20a%20vacant%201970s%20office%20building%20in%20downtown%20Philadelphia%2C%20it%20fully%20reconstructed%20the%20facade%20and%20windows.%20It%20also%20solved%20some%20of%20the%20problems%20associated%20with%20a%20large%20floor%20plan%20by%20creating%20smaller%20amenity%20spaces%20on%20several%20floors%20occupying%20many%20of%20the%20windowless%20spaces%20in%20the%20center%20of%20the%20building%2C%20Paynter%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farchitects-explain-how-old-offices-become-luxury-real-estate-renovations-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693826401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0fdfc5114270019aec812%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farchitects-explain-how-old-offices-become-lu