%20Pillow%20Fight%20Championship.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Kleeblatt%2FPFC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHauley%20Tillman%20won%20the%20Pillow%20Fight%20Championship%20in%202022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20used%20the%20%245%2C000%20in%20winnings%20to%20open%20a%20dojo%20in%20the%20Miami%20neighborhood%20where%20he%20grew%20up.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETillman%20holds%20black%20belts%20in%20numerous%20martial%20arts%20and%20loves%20working%20with%20kids.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%26quot%3BChamp%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhauleytillman19%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3EHauley%20Tillman%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%2035%2C%20a%20father%20of%20two%20and%20a%20martial%20artist%20from%20Miami's%20Liberty%20City%20neighborhood.%20He%20relied%20on%20his%20martial%20arts%20skills%20to%20help%20him%20win%20the%20Pillow%20Fight%20Championship%2C%20or%20PFC%2C%20bracket%20in%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETillman%20then%20used%20the%20%245%2C000%20in%20prize%20money%20to%20help%20start%20a%20dojo%2C%20the%20Mighty%20Warriorz%2C%20where%20he%20teaches%20neighborhood%20children%20and%20adults.%20He%20began%20exploring%20martial%20arts%20as%20a%20teenager%20after%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Miami-Dade%20Schools%20Police%20Department%20and%20an%20expert%20in%20martial%20arts%20named%20Steven%20Tarrago%20suggested%20Tillman%20do%20so.%20The%20conversation%20was%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20in%20martial%20arts%20before%20PFC.%20I%20became%20a%20black%20belt%20under%20Master%20Steven%20Tarrago.%20Basically%2C%20it%20started%20when%20I%20was%20homeless.%20I%20was%20a%20homeless%20kid%20%E2%80%94%20like%20maybe%2016.%20I%20always%20knew%20how%20to%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20just%20shadowboxing%20in%20the%20park%20and%20these%20police%20just%20rolled%20up%20on%20me%20and%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20in%20trouble%20or%20something.%20But%20Master%20Tarrago%20was%20just%20watching%20me%20train%20because%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I'd%20go%20to%20the%20park%20every%20day%20and%20I'd%20kick%20and%20do%20my%20shadow-boxing%20stuff.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20telling%20me%20that%20day%20that%20I%20looked%20really%20good%20and%20that%20he%20had%20a%20school.%20Master%20Tarrago%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMatter%20of%20fact%2C%20I'm%20gonna%20be%20here%20tomorrow%20at%20such%20and%20such%20time%20to%20pick%20you%20up.%26quot%3B%20And%20I%20really%20thought%20he%20was%20bullcrap.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BHe's%20not%20gonna%20come.%26quot%3B%20I%20had%20tattoos%20everywhere%3B%20I%20was%20a%20product%20of%20my%20environment.%20But%20he%20pulled%20up%20in%20the%20police%20car%20and%20took%20me%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20really%20far.%20So%20he%20used%20to%20come%20and%20get%20me%20in%20a%20police%20car%20every%20single%20day%20and%20take%20me%20up%20there%20to%20Twin%20Dragons%2C%20his%20dojo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20the%20only%20Black%20kid%20in%20the%20school.%20He%20trained%20me%20and%20I%20was%20destroying%20everybody.%20In%20my%20first%20tournament%2C%20I%20had%20an%20ankle%20bracelet%20on%20%E2%80%94%20making%20sure%20I%20wasn't%20getting%20into%20trouble.%20I%20remember%2C%20Master%20Tarrago%2C%20he%20got%20some%20Ace%20bandages%20and%20wrapped%20it%20up%20and%20told%20me%20to%20go%20out%20there%20and%20fight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20trust%20him%20with%20my%20life.%20He's%20like%20not%20just%20my%20master.%20He's%20like%20my%20brother%2C%20you%20know.%20He%20basically%20gave%20me%20a%20chance%20to%20become%20a%20better%20person.%20I%20know%20without%20him%20giving%20me%20that%20chance%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20here%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224781%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hauley%20Tillman%20in%20the%20Pillow%20Fight%20Championship%5C%22%20ch