6quot%3BHey%2C%20we've%20got%20a%20PFC%20tournament%20going.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BUh%2C%20you're%20gonna%20pay%20me%20to%20hit%20somebody%20with%20a%20pillow%3F%26quot%3B%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BAwesome.%26quot%3B%20You%20know%2C%20I've%20been%20doing%20pillow%20fighting%20since%20I%20was%20a%20kid.%20We%20didn't%20really%20have%20too%20many%20toys%20and%20stuff%20like%20that%20so%20a%20pillow%20fight%20was%20like%20a%20thing%20growing%20up.%20And%20I'd%20be%20kicking%20my%20brothers%20and%20sisters%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0everybody's%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0butts%20ever%20since%20by%20me%20being%20a%20blackbelt.%20And%20in%20kung%20fu%2C%20I%20studied%20a%20lot%20of%20katas%20and%20different%20forms%20with%20nunchucks.%20So%20I%20just%20feel%20like%20I%20mastered%20the%20PFC.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20can't%20just%20go%20into%20a%20pillow%20fight%20thinking%20it's%20gonna%20be%20easy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWell%2C%20I'm%20very%20active%20but%20by%20my%20first%20pillow%20fight%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20you%20have%20to%20use%20a%20lot%20of%20motion%20and%20you%20have%20to%20have%20some%20type%20of%20cardio.%20You%20can't%20just%20go%20into%20thinking%20it's%20gonna%20be%20easy.%20I%20thought%20it%20was%20just%20gonna%20be%20like%2C%20you%20know%2C%20a%20really%20easy%20thing%20to%20do.%20I%20thought%20I%20could%20run%20through%20it.%20But%20you%20really%20have%20to%20have%20some%20type%20of%20technique.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20my%20skill%20set%20with%20the%20nunchucks%C2%A0and%20I%20also%20realized%20that%20you%20do%20need%20cardio.%20I've%20seen%20guys%20get%20knocked%20out%20with%20a%20pillow%20before%20just%20because%20they%20were%20tired.%20It's%20really%20tough.%20I%20just%20trained%20a%20lot.%20I%20did%20a%20lot%20more%20running%20and%20calisthenics.%20I%20worked%20out%20with%20my%20weapons%2C%20with%20my%20heavy%20bo%20staff%2C%20and%2C%20of%20course%2C%20with%20my%20nunchucks.%20They%20weigh%20at%20least%20like%20three%20and%20a%20half%20pounds.%20And%20the%20pillow%20is%20like%20two%20pounds%20so%20when%20I%20actually%20fight%2C%20it's%20really%20light.%20So%20I%20have%20a%20real%20advantage%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20wanted%20to%20win%20the%20PFC%20so%20I%20could%20open%20a%20dojo%20in%20my%20neighborhood%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20I%20wanted%20to%20give%20back%20to%20my%20neighborhood%20about%20seven%20or%20eight%20years%20ago%20after%20I%20got%20stabbed%20through%20my%20abdominal%20muscle%20and%20my%20liver.%20I%20was%20really%20close%20to%20death.%20Once%20I%20was%20done%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20God%20gave%20me%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20I%20know%20God%20gave%20me%20%E2%80%94%20a%20second%20chance.%20And%20I%20just%20really%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20martial%20arts%20and%20I%20humbled%20down.%20I%20was%20less%20angry.%20You%20know%2C%20I%20really%20saw%20life%20for%20what%20it%20was.%20And%20people%20started%20wanting%20me%20to%20teach%20them%20and%20I%20had%20one%20kid%20who%20was%20always%20coming%20by%20anytime%20when%20I%20was%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20opened%20the%20dojo%20once%20I%20got%20the%20funds%20for%20the%20PFC.%20I%20heard%20people%20laughing%2C%20making%20jokes%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20guy%20says%20he's%20gonna%20win%20the%20whole%20thing.%20And%20he's%20going%20to%20open%20up%20a%20jiu-jitsu%20school.%26quot%3B%20Well%2C%20to%20each%20his%20own.%20They%20were%20laughing%20about%20it%2C%20but%20they%20don't%20understand.%20Where%20I%20come%20from%2C%20kids%20don't%20have%20chances%2C%20like%20how%20other%20kids%20have.%20We%20get%20looked%20past%20a%20lot.%20That's%20what%20I%20would%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20told%20them.%20I%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI'm%20gonna%20beat%20everybody.%20I'm%20going%20to%20destroy%20everybody.%20And%20I'm%20going%20to%20open%20up%20the%20school.%26quot%3B%20That's%20what%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20teach%20over%2060%20students%20in%20total%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0kids%20and%20adults.%20M