ng%20so%20can%20convey%20respect%20toward%20the%20subject%20and%20make%20the%20production%20go%20more%20smoothly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20fact%20that%20life%20story%20acquisitions%20have%20entered%20the%20popular%20consciousness%20has%20spurred%20the%20widespread%20belief%20that%20any%20portrayal%20of%20a%20factual%20series%20of%20events%20entitles%20those%20depicted%20to%20a%20lucrative%20payday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20expectation%20increases%20production%20costs%20and%20the%20risk%20of%20litigation%2C%20thereby%20deterring%20otherwise%20worthwhile%20projects%20and%20depriving%20the%20public%20of%20meaningful%20content%20that%20is%20based%20on%20true%20stories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20could%20be%20done%20about%20this%20situation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20idea%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D4480628%5C%22%3Ethat%20we%E2%80%99ve%20written%20about%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0would%20prevent%20right%20of%20publicity%20laws%20%E2%80%93%20the%20basis%20for%20many%20life%20story%20lawsuits%20%E2%80%93%20from%20being%20used%20against%20works%20that%20convey%20ideas%20and%20tell%20a%20story%2C%20such%20as%20books%2C%20films%20and%20TV%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20important%20thing%20that%20can%20be%20done%2C%20though%2C%20is%20educating%20people%20that%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20right%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20every%20description%20of%20the%20events%20of%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollective%20history%2C%20in%20our%20view%2C%20belongs%20in%20the%20public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EJorge%20L.%20Contreras%2C%20James%20T.%20Jensen%20Endowed%20Professor%20for%20Transactional%20Law%20and%20Director%2C%20Program%20on%20Intellectual%20Property%20and%20Technology%20Law%2C%20University%20of%20Utah%3B%20and%20Dave%20Fagundes%2C%20Baker%20Botts%20LLP%20Professor%20of%20Law%20and%20Research%20Dean%2C%20University%20of%20Houston%20Law%20Center.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20republished%20from%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20Conversation%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0under%20a%20Creative%20Commons%20license.%20Read%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheconversation.com%2Fmichael-oher-mike-tyson-and-the-question-of-whether-you-own-your-life-story-212242%5C%22%3Eoriginal%20article%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693824313000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04154720%2FMike-Tyson.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fcan-you-own-your-life-story%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Life%20story%20acquisitions%E2%80%99%20have%20led%20to%20the%20belief%20that%20any%20portrayal%20of%20a%20factual%20series%20of%20events%20entitles%20those%20depicted%20to%20a%20lucrative%20payday.%20But%20is%20this%20true%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fcan-you-own-your-life-story%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi's%20Palam%20Airbase%20To%20Welcome%20Air%20Force%20One%2C%2070%20VVIP%20Jets%20For%20G20%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20has%20made%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20arrangements%26quot%3B%20to%20land%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20nearly%2070%20VVIP%20aircraft%20at%20the%20Palam%20Technical%20Airport%20-%20an%20airbase%20-%20when%20world%20leaders%20begin%20arriving%20in%20India%20for%20the%20mega%20G20%20Summit%20later%20this%20week.%20Four%20other%20airports%20-%20identified%20as%20%26quot%3Breserved%20airports%26quot%3B%20-%20have%20been%20marked%20for%20any%20contingencies%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarting%20September%207%2C%20the%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20fighter%20planes%20will%20be%20on%20standby%20to%20keep%20a%20close%20watch%20on%20any%20suspicious%20activity%20in%20the%20Delhi%20sky%2C%20including%20of%20UAVs%20or%20drones%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20functionary%20in%20the%20government%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BContingency%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20in%20Lucknow%2C%20Jaipur%2C%20Indore%2C%20and%20Amritsar%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20PK%20Mishra%2C%20the%20Principal%20Secretary%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20and%20Delhi's%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Vinai%20Kumar%20Saxena%20oversaw%20the%20arrangements%20at%20Palam%20Technical%20Airport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four%20reserved%20airports%20were%20identified%20at%20a%20high-level%20meeting%20with%20officials%20from%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%2C%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20the%20Bureau%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20Security%20(BCAS)%2C%20the%20Central%20Industrial%20Security%20Force%20(CISF)%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi%20International%20Airport%20Limited%20(DIAL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Air%20Traffic%20Control%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20be%20on%20high%20alert%20during%20the%20G20%20Summit%20and%20closely%20monitor%20all%20flights%20entering%20Delhi.%20In%20case%20of%20any%20emergency%20situation%2C%20flights%20will%20be%20diverted%20to%20any%20of%20the%20four%20other%20airports%20that%20are%20part%20of%20the%20contingency%20plan%2C%26quot%3B%20another%20senior%20official%20handling%20G20%20security%20arrangements%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20VIPs%20will%20land%20at%20the%20technical%20airport%20but%20aircraft%20and%20private%20jets%20carrying%20them%20will%20be%20parked%20at%20the%20Delhi%20airport.%20Special%20arrangements%20have%20been%20made%20to%20park%20the%20Air%20Force%20One%20and%20a%20few%20other%20important%20aircraft%20at%20the%20Palam%20Air%20Force%20Station.%20The%20station%20is%20under%20the%20security%20of%20the%20Air%20Force%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20officer%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Defence%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20these%20VVIP%20aircraft%20will%20be%20parked%20in%20Bay-1%20and%20Bay-3%20of%20the%20Delhi%20airport%20as%20they%20are%20very%20close%20to%20the%20ceremonial%20lounge%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20him%2C%20parking%20spaces%20have%20been%20identified%20at%20the%20airport%2C%20Terminal-1%2C%20and%20the%20cargo%20terminal.%20%26quot%3BAround%2018%20aircraft%20will%20be%20accommodated%20at%20the%20Palam%20base%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20G20%20Summit%2C%20we%20have%20already%20made%20provisions%20for%20the%20required%20parking%20of%20aircraft%20at%20Delhi%20Airport.%20Our%20top%20priority%20remains%20ensuring%20a%20smooth%20and%20efficient%20travel%20experience%20for%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20further%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Airport%20boasts%20an%20impressive%20parking%20capacity%20of%2072%20charter%20aircraft%2C%20along%20with%20a%20dedicated%20terminal.%20The%20DIAL%20officials%20maintained%20that%20the%20current%20flight%20cancellations%20were%20not%20linked%20to%20the%20availability%20of%20parking%20spaces%20for%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20received%20requests%20from%20airlines%20for%20the%20cancellation%20of%20approximately%2080%20arrivals%20and%2080%20departures%20as%20of%20now.%20However%2C%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20working%20closely%20with%20airlines%20to%20minimize%20any%20inconvenience%20caused%20to%20passengers%2C%26quot%3B%20stated%20an%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20reassure%20all%20travellers%20that%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20is%20fully%20equipped%20with%20ample%20parking%20for%20aircraft.%20Despite%20the%20cancellations%2C%20we%20are%20pleased%20to%20report%20that%20the%20restrictions%20will%20not%20impact%20international%20flights.%20The%20cancellations%20only%20account%20for%20approximately%20six%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20normal%20domestic%20operations%20at%20the%20Delhi%20Airport%20over%20the%20span%20of%20thre