ng%20people%2C%20these%20days%2C%20aspire%20to%20save%20and%20invest%20enough%20money%20so%20they%20can%20retire%20early.%20One%20such%20person%20is%C2%A0Ethan%20Nguonly%2C%20a%2022-year-old%20software%20engineer%20at%20Google%2C%20who%20is%20aiming%20for%20an%20early%20retirement%20with%20a%20target%20of%20accumulating%20%245%20million%20(roughly%20Rs%2041%20crore)%20by%20the%20age%20of%2035%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2023%2F08%2F31%2F22-year-old-earns-194k-a-year-as-a-software-engineer-at-google.html%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20young%20techie%2C%20%C2%A0living%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California%2C%20credited%20his%20parents%20for%C2%A0teaching%20him%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20investing%20money%20in%20stocks%20rather%20than%20just%20saving%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''%E2%80%B3%5BMy%20parents%5D%20really%20explained%20it%20to%20me%20well%2C%20They%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98If%20you%20leave%20your%20money%20here%20%5Bin%20a%20savings%20account%5D%2C%20over%20time%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20become%20worthless%2C'%20and%20they%20said%20that%20you%20should%20really%20learn%20to%20invest%20it%20into%20something%2C''%20Mr%20Nguonly%20told%20%3Cem%3ECNBC%20Make%20It.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20was%20younger%2C%20the%20main%20thing%20I%20was%20thinking%20about%20was%2C%20'All%20this%20money%20keeps%20getting%20bigger%2C%20keeps%20growing%2C%20and%20I'm%20not%20doing%20any%20work%20for%20this%2C'.%C2%A0This%20really%20exposed%20me%20to%20the%20idea%20that%20my%20investments%20could%20make%20me%20money%20instead%20of%20me%20actually%20having%20to%20actively%20work%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20determination%20to%20achieve%20financial%20freedom%20led%20him%20to%C2%A0complete%20his%20computer%20science%20degree%20at%20the%20University%20of%20California%2C%20Berkeley%2C%20in%20just%20two%20years%2C%20avoiding%20student%20debt.%20He%20also%20opted%20to%20stay%20with%20his%20family%20after%20completing%20his%20bachelor's%20degree%20to%20save%20money%20on%20rent.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20then%C2%A0secured%20a%20job%20at%20a%20software%20company%20while%20simultaneously%20starting%20his%C2%A0master's%20degree%20in%C2%A0information%20and%20data%20science.%20He%20completed%20the%20course%20in%20August%202022.%20In%20the%20midst%20of%20getting%20his%20master's%2C%20he%20also%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20Google%20as%20a%20software%20engineer.%20He%20has%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20%24194%2C000%20(roughly%20Rs%201.60%20crore)%2C%20inclusive%20of%20bonuses%20and%20stock%20units.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%C2%A0he%20also%20has%20close%20to%20%24135%2C000%20(Rs%C2%A01.11%20crore)%20invested%20across%20his%20retirement%20and%20other%20investment%20accounts%2C%20as%20well%20as%20homes%20in%20Florida%20and%20California.%20He%20aims%20to%20invest%2035%25%20of%20his%20take-home%20pay%20each%20year%20and%20plans%20to%20expand%20his%20real%20estate%20portfolio%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr.%20Nguonly%20bought%20an%20investment%20property%20in%20Riverview%2C%20Florida%20at%20the%20start%20of%202022%20and%20about%20a%20year%20later%2C%20bought%20his%20primary%20residence%20in%20La%20Palma%2C%20California%20where%20he%20lives%20with%20his%20dog.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20spend%20too%20much%20money%20on%20food%20because%20Google%20provides%20free%20breakfast%20and%20lunch.%20Further%2C%20he%20doesn't%20believe%20in%20splurging%20on%20brand-name%20clothes%20and%20prefers%20to%20wear%20simplistic%20and%20affordable%20clothes.%20While%20he%20loves%20traveling%20and%20usually%20takes%20three%20to%20four%20trips%20a%20year%2C%20he%20sticks%20to%20lower-cost%20options%20rather%20than%20luxury%20upgrades%2C%C2%A0such%20as%20sharing%20an%20Airbnb%20with%20a%20friend.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20reach%20his%20%245%20million%20goal%2C%20he%20plans%20to%20continue%20investing%20in%20his%20retirement%20accounts%20and%20adding%20to%20his%20real%20estate%20portfolio%20by%20buying%20a%20new%20property%20every%20couple%20of%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20a%20book%20that%20really%20inspired%20him%20on%20his%20journey%2C%20he%20said%2C%20''It%20talks%20about%20how%20you%20should%20spend%20more%20money%20on%20experiences%20and%20travel%20while%20you're%20still%20young%20and%20healthy.%20This%20is%20why%20I%20really%20set%20out%20this%20goal.%C2%A0I%20don't%20want%20to%20be%2067%20years%20old%20trying%20to%20climb%20up%20some%20mountain%2C%20I'd%20rather%20do%20it%20while%20I'm%20still%20able%20to%20fully%20enjoy%20these%20experiences.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F40cmfqso_google-generic_625x300_04_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20has%20an%20annual%20income%20of%20%24194%2C000%20(roughly%20Rs%201.60%20crore)%2C%20inclusive%20of%20bonuses%20and%20stock%20units.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fgoogle-software-engineer-22-plans-to-retire-at-35-with-savings-of-rs-41-crore-heres-how-4358204%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20UK's%20biggest%20grocery%20chain%20is%20offering%20body%20cameras%20to%20staff%20as%20it%20seeks%20to%20fight%20the%20'sc