orkers%2C%26quot%3B%20Tesco%20CEO%20Ken%20Murphy%20wrote%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fdebate%2Farticle-12474181%2Fstaff-deserve-safe-work-Tesco-KEN-MURPHY.html%23comments%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopinion%20piece%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20The%20Mail%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20time%20we%20put%20an%20end%20to%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20though%20only%20a%20small%20number%20of%20customers%20are%20verbally%20and%20physically%20abusive%20towards%20staff%2C%20they%20have%20a%20%26quot%3Bdisproportionate%20impact.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20these%20colleagues%2C%20their%20families%2C%20and%20all%20of%20us%20who%20know%20someone%20who%20works%20in%20retail%2C%20it's%20heartbreaking%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20continued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20Tesco%20has%20invested%20%C2%A344%20million%20(about%20%2455.6%20million)%20on%20security%20measures%20including%20door%20access%20systems%2C%20protection%20screens%2C%20and%20digital%20radios%2C%20Murphy%20said.%20But%20he%20emphasized%20that%20other%20changes%20were%20needed%20to%20deter%20criminals%20in%20the%20first%20place%2C%20including%20better%20cooperation%20between%20police%20and%20businesses.%20He%20also%20demanded%20changes%20in%20the%20law%2C%20such%20as%20making%20abuse%20and%20violence%20towards%20retail%20workers%20a%20specific%20offence%20in%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20British%20grocery%20chains%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fuk-66699084%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESainsbury's%2C%20the%20Co-op%2C%20and%20Waitrose%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20also%20offered%20body%20cameras%20to%20staff.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fretail-crime-waitrose-john-lewis-free-coffee-cops-deter-shoplifters-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWaitrose%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20begun%20offering%20uniformed%20officers%20free%20hot%20drinks%20in%20a