p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDivorced%20from%20its%20present%20political%20context%2C%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20not%20welcome%20the%20proposal%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections.%20The%20move%20will%20halve%20the%20presently%20crippling%20electioneering%20expenses%20for%20political%20parties.%20And%20by%20extension%2C%20the%20need%20to%20raise%20money%2C%20much%20of%20which%20has%20been%20coming%20from%20clandestine%20and%20criminal%20sources%20ever%20since%20the%20ban%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Indira%20Gandhi%20put%20on%20company%20donations%20to%20political%20parties%20in%201970.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReunification%20of%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20also%20make%20it%20far%20easier%20for%20a%20future%20government%20to%20set%20up%20a%20state%20financed%20and%20publicly%20audited%20system%20of%20election%20financing.%20This%20would%20not%20only%20weaken%20and%2C%20over%20time%2C%20eliminate%20the%20nexus%20between%20crime%20and%20politics%20in%20the%20country%2C%20but%20also%20open%20the%20way%20for%20reforms%20in%20the%20police%20and%20lower%20administration%20that%20will%20cleanse%20the%20government%20of%20corruption%20and%20make%20it%20serve%20the%20people.%20It%20would%20also%20lengthen%20the%20time%20horizon%20over%20which%20government%20policies%20will%20need%20to%20bear%20fruit%3B%20restore%20the%20Centre-State%20co-ordination%20in%20policy%20making%20that%20was%20severely%20weakened%20by%20the%20separation%20of%20central%20from%20state%20elections%2C%20and%20facilitate%20structural%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felections-2024-india-most-dangerous-phase%5C%22%3EAs%20the%202024%20Elections%20Approach%2C%20India%20Is%20Entering%20the%20Most%20Dangerous%20Phase%20of%20Its%20Existence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20enacted%20with%20necessary%20safeguards%2C%20it%20will%20also%20put%20a%20brake%20on%20opportunistic%20defections%20from%20political%20parties.%20The%20most%20necessary%20of%20these%20safeguards%20will%20be%20an%20automatic%20declaration%20of%20President%E2%80%99s%20rule%20till%20the%20next%20general%20election%20in%20any%20state%20where%20the%20government%20has%20been%20brought%20down%20by%20defections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20reasons%20for%20taking%20this%20sudden%20decision%2C%20however%2C%20have%20little%20to%20do%20with%20better%20governance.%20He%20has%20taken%20it%20because%20he%20is%20aware%20that%20the%20BJP%20runs%20the%20risk%20of%20suffering%20the%20same%20fate%20in%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%20elections%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20possibly%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20that%20it%20suffered%20in%20Karnataka.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20is%20therefore%20understandably%20wary%20of%20going%20into%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20with%20a%20string%20of%20electoral%20defeats%20in%20major%20states%20behind%20him.%20So%20he%20has%20decided%20to%20kill%20two%20birds%20with%20one%20stone%20%E2%80%93%20avoid%20four%20important%20state%20elections%20that%20his%20party%20could%20lose%2C%20and%20hold%20a%20combined%20national%20and%20state%20election%20with%20the%20prestige%20of%20the%20G-20%20presidency%20and%20its%20grand%20conference%20in%20Delhi%20to%20buoy%20him%2C%20delivering%20both%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20state%20to%20his%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fone-nation-one-election-fourth-committee%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98One%20Nation%2C%20One%20Election%E2%80%99%2C%20Fourth%20Committee%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20INDIA%20coalition%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20for%20the%20one-election%20proposal%20is%20therefore%20understandable.%20But%20it%20is%20also%20short-sighted%20because%20unifying%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20will%20resolve%20the%20most%20knotty%20problem%20that%20the%20alliance%20is%20facing%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20next%20general%20election%20and%20greatly%20improve%20its%20chances%20of%20victory.%20This%20problem%20is%20the%20allocation%20of%20seats%20to%20its%20constituent%20parties%20in%20each%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20Mumbai%20meeting%20showed%2C%20the%20coalition%20is%20determined%20to%20field%20only%20one%20candidate%20against%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20in%20each%20constituency.%20But%20it%20has%20yet%20to%20decide%20from%20which%20party%2C%20and%20on%20what%20basis%20the%20candidate%20should%20be%20chosen.%20At%20the%20Patna%20meeting%2C%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamta%20Bannerjee%20had%20told%20the%20press%20that%20the%20alliance%20would%20set%20up%20coordination%20committees%20that%20would%20first%20decide%20the%20principles%20they%20would%20follow%20in%20the%20selection%20of%20candidates%20and%20then%20use%20these%20to%20choose%20the%20party%20and%20candidate%20for%20each%20constituency.%20Today%2C%20two%20more%20alliance%20meetings%20later%2C%20that%20process%20is%20only%20about%20to%20begin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20foot-dragging%20is%20taking%20place%20because%20the%20party%20leaders%20have%20not%20found%20a%20way%20to%20cross%20the%20main%20hurdle%20they%20face%3A%20how%20to%20retain%20the%20loyalty%20and%20support%20of%20their%20cadres%20in%20the%20constituencies%20that%20they%20have%20ceded%20to%20an%20ally%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20problem%20would%20not%20have%20arisen%20if%20there%20had%20been%20a%20system%20of%20state%20financing%20of%20elections%20like%20the%20one%20Western%20Europe.%20In%20its%20absence%2C%20parties%20have%20come%20to%20rely%20on%20local%20financiers%20whom%20they%20offer%20government%20contracts%20and%20other%20favours%20if%20their%20party%20comes%20to%20power.%20This%20clientelist%20system%20starts%20breaking%20down%20if%20the%20financiers%20lose%20faith%20in%20the%20party%2C%20or%20in%20its%20candidate%E2%80%99s%20capacity%20to%20win.%20It%20ceases%20to%20exist%20when%20the%20party%20has%20no%20horse%20in%20the%20race.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBy%20offering%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections%20Modi%20has%20unwittingly%20offered%20INDIA%20a%20way%20out%20of%20its%20dilemma.%20This%20would%20confine%20the%20seat%20sharing%20between%20political%20parties%20only%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20and%20allow%20full%20competition%20to%20continue%20between%20them%20sin%20the%20various%20state%20assemblies%20and%20also%20require%20them%20to%20make%20a%20clear%20demarcation%20between%20national%20and%20local%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EParty%20cadres%20can%20then%20be%20instructed%20to%20emphasise%20national%20issues%20in%20parliamentary%20constituencies%20where%20their%20party%20is%20fielding%20candidates%20for%20both%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Vidhan%20Sabha%2C%20and%20to%20place%20greater%20stress%20on%20state%20and%20local%20issues%20in%20those%20where%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20has%20been%20allotted%20to%20another%20member%20of%20the%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprem-shankar-jha%5C%22%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693823434000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F28185418%2FScreenshot-2023-06-28-at-6.53.02-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-opposition-stands-to-gain-more-from-modis-move-to-unify-elections%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22By%20offering%20to%20reunite%20central%20and%20state%20elections%2C%20Modi%20has%