3Cp%3EBorrowers%20have%20already%20reported%20issues%20with%20repayment.%20One%20borrower%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-payments-resume-confusion-borrowers-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3Epreviously%20told%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20her%20student-loan%20company%20projected%20a%20%2449%2C000%20monthly%20payment%20%E2%80%94%20which%20the%20company%20admitted%20was%20a%20mistake%20%E2%80%94%20but%20she's%20still%20waiting%20for%20her%20statement%20to%20be%20corrected.%20To%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20it's%20been%20increasingly%20difficult%20for%20borrowers%20to%20get%20ahold%20of%20the%20companies%20that%20manage%20their%20debt.%20One%20servicer%2C%20Nelnet%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-company-website-call-center-shut-down-borrowers-payments-2023-8%5C%22%3Ehas%20had%20to%20shut%20down%20its%20call%20center%20and%20website%20multiple%20times%3C%2Fa%3E%20following%20an%20influx%20of%20requests%20from%20borrowers%2C%20leaving%20many%20unable%20to%20access%20their%20accounts%20and%20determine%20their%20repayment%20schedules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarolyn%20Fast%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20The%20Century%20Foundation%20who%20focuses%20on%20higher-education%20policy%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20some%20borrowers%20have%20never%20had%20to%20make%20payments%20on%20their%20loans%20because%20of%20the%20pandemic%20pause%2C%20and%20after%20three%20years%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20really%20big%20job%26quot%3B%20in%20facilitating%20this%20transition.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20lot%20of%20confusion%20and%20questions%20that%20borrowers%20have%20about%20what%20their%20obligations%20and%20options%20are%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Fast%20said.%20%26quot%3BMany%20are%20worried%20that%20it%20could%20be%20a%20perfect%20storm%20of%20bureaucratic%20obstacles%20for%20borrowers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThose%20obstacles%20will%20likely%20include%20a%20lack%20of%20resources%20and%20funding%20for%20the%20Education%20Department%2C%20paperwork%20issues%20for%20borrowers%2C%20and%20inflation%20that%20could%20strain%20borrowers'%20budgets%20as%20they%20attempt%20to%20foot%20another%20monthly%20bill.%20An%20Education%20Department%20spokesperson%20recently%20told%20Insider%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20to%20regularly%20communicate%20with%20borrowers%20and%20share%20repayment%20options%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-student-loan-repayment-plan-debt-relief-repayment-save-idr-2023-8%5C%22%3Ethe%20new%20SAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20intended%20to%20make%20payments%20more%20affordable.%20The%20agency%20also%20said%20it%20remains%20in%20frequent%20contact%20with%20servicers%20to%20ensure%20they%20directly%20communicate%20repayment%20information%20to%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20%26quot%3Bthey're%20trying%20to%20do%20whatever%20they%20can%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20runs%20smoothly%2C%26quot%3B%20Fast%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20still%20going%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20challenge%20for%20the%20department.%26quot%3B%20Here%20are%20the%20challenges%20borrowers%20could%20encounter%20as%20they%20begin%20to%20make%20payments%20again%20this%20fall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'This%20could%20be%20a%20huge%20shock%20to%20their%20budgets'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Biden%20intended%20for%20borrowers%20to%20restart%20payments%20with%20a%20reduction%20to%20their%20balances%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20June%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-blocked-supreme-court-strikes-down-debt-cancellation-2023-5%5C%22%3Estruck%20down%20his%20plan%20to%20cancel%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20federal%20student%20debt%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Stephanie%20Hall%2C%20the%20acting%20senior%20director%20of%20higher%20education%20policy%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20American%20Progress%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20Biden's%20debt-relief%20plan%20%26quot%3Bwould%20have%20actually%20cleared%20out%20a%20certain%20number%20of%20borrowers%20from%20the%20system%2C%20which%20would%20have%20lightened%20the%20projected%20amount%20of%20need%20for%20servicer%20hours%20and%20for%20call-center%20hours%20for%20the%20primary%20services.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20more%20borrowers%20in%20the%20system%20currently%20than%20what%20the%20Biden%20administration%20might%20have%20previously%20projected%20for%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20issue%20Hall%20said%20she's%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20is%20the%20impact%20the%20resumption%20will%20have%20on%20borrowers'%20budgets%2C%20especially%20with%20high%20inflation%20levels.%20While%20inflation%20has%20slowed%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20the%20latest%20Consumer%20Price%20Index%20reading%2C%20which%20measures%20inflation%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpowell-jackson-hole-next-interest-rate-decision-fed-inflation-2023-8%5C%22%3Erose%203.2%25%20year%20over%20year%20in%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20could%20pose%20difficulties%20for%20borrowers%20as%20they%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20afford%20an%20extra%20monthly%20payment%20on%20top%20of%20their%20other%20usual%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20could%20be%20a%20huge%20shock%20to%20their%20budgets%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20said.%20%26quot%3BBefore%20the%20pandemic%2C%20borrowers%20were%20already%20choosing%20between%20meeting%20their%20own%20basic%20needs%20and%20making%20their%20student-loan%20payments.%20But%20the%20pandemic%20pause%20has%20gone%20on%20for%20so%20long%20that%20household%20budgets%20really%20changed%20during%20the%20past%20three%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe%20before%20the%20pause%2C%20they%20couldn't%20get%20a%20mortgage%20and%20now%20they%20have%20one%2C%20or%20they%20took%20on%20other%20forms%20of%20personal%20debt%2C%20and%20then%20inflation%20has%20also%20impacted%20how%20far%20our%20budget%20can%20stretch%2C%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20added.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I%20think%20all%20of%20those%20factors%20on%20top%20of%20now%20turning%20the%20student-loan%20system%20back%20on%20and%20having%20this%20additional%20bill%20come%20to%20you%20monthly%20is%20going%20to%20make%20a%20great%20deal%20of%20folks%20have%20to%20make%20some%20difficult%20choices%20in%20their%20budgets.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20needs%20more%20money%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20all%20comes%20down%20to%20money%2C%20and%20the%20Education%20Department%20needs%20more%20of%20it.%20Scott%20Buchanan%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20Student%20Loan%20Servicing%20Alliance%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20that%20represents%20federal%20servicers%20%E2%80%94%20previously%20told%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20only%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20resources%20to%20provide%20staffing%20and%20when%20we%20have%20these%20huge%20spikes%20because%20of%20some%20sort%20of%20communications%2C%20then%20there's%20not%20an%20ability%20to%20really%20provide%20any%20more%20resources%2C%20because%20the%20government%20doesn't%20have%20those%20resources.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20something%20Biden's%20administration%20is%20well%20aware%20of.%20The%20Office%20of%20Management%20and%20Budget's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-funding-social-security-student-loan-repayment-wic-food-benefits-2023-8%5C%22%3Elatest%20funding%20request%20to%20Congress%3C%2Fa%3E%20noted%20that%20without%20increased%20funding%2C%20%26quot%3Bbasic%20ongoing%20activities%20including%20loan%20servicing%20operations%2C%20Free%20Application%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%20application%20processing%2C%20common%20origination%20and%20disbursement%20activities%2C%20data%20center%20hosting%2C%20and%20call%20center%20operations%20will%20be%20impeded.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Republicans'%20recent%20budget%20proposal%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-repayment-more-hurdles-gop-budget-cut-proposal-2023-7%5C%22%3Eincluded%20a%20funding%20cut%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20suggesting%20more%20challenges%20to%20come%20in%20administering%20repayment%20and%20relief%20programs%20for%20borrowers.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20resource-strapped%20a%20servicer%20is%20and%20the%20more%20resource-strapped%20FSA%20is%2C%20the%20heightened%20concerns%20we%20have%20for%20that%20treatment%20of%20borrowers%20and%20just%20for%20the%20accuracy%20on%20the%20part%20of%20servicers%20giving%20information%20to%20borrowers%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFast%20also%20noted%20that%20minimal%20resources%20will%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20the%20department%20to%C2%A0ensure%20servicers%20are%20communicating%20with%20borrowers%20effectively%2C%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bthey%20don't%20have%20a%20lot%20in%20their%20budget%20to%20put%20toward%20this%20sort%20of%20oversight%20that%20they're%20going%20to%20need%20to%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20give%20borrowers%20some%20relief%2C%20the%20department%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdo-i-have-to-resume-student-loan-payments-debt-relief-2023-7%5C%22%3Ea%2012-month%20%26quot%3Bon-ramp%26quot%3B%20period%3C%2Fa%3E%20starting%20in%20October%2C%20during%20which%20missed%20payments%20will%20not%20be%20reported%20to%20credit%20agencies.%20In%20the%20meantime%2C%20the%20department%20recommends%20borrowers%20make%20their%20payments%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhere-does-student-loan-forgiveness-stand-biden-debt-relief-borrowers-2023-8%5C%22%3Ewait%20for%20Biden's%20new%20plan%20for%20broad%20debt%20relief.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-facing-perfect-storm-repayment-debt-relief-biden-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdi