ucture%20that%20allows%20them%20to%20provide%20appropriate%2C%20necessary%2C%20and%20sorely%20needed%20medical%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20Mason%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat%20the%20strike%20could%20mean%20for%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20patients%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Coalition%20of%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20Unions%20represents%20employees%20across%20dozens%20of%20roles%20at%20the%20company%2C%20including%20admissions%20staff%2C%20cleaners%2C%20phlebotomists%2C%20surgery%20assistants%2C%20and%20others.%20The%20union%20doesn't%20represent%20the%20company's%20doctors%20and%20registered%20nurses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20all%20those%20essential%20employees%20went%20on%20strike%2C%20it%20could%20bring%20some%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhealthy.kaiserpermanente.org%2Flearn%2Fwhat-is-kaiser-permanente%5C%22%3EKaiser%20Permanente's%2039%20hospitals%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%20stand-still%2C%20according%20to%20Keven%20Dardon%2C%20a%20union%20organizer%20and%20a%20patient%20access%20representative%20for%20a%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20hospital%20in%20Oregon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20very%20detrimental%20for%20our%20patients%2C%26quot%3B%20Dardon%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHospitals%20would%20not%20be%20the%20only%20facilities%20impacted.%20The%20Coalition%20also%20represents%20pharmacists%2C%20pharmacy%20techs%2C%20social%20workers%2C%20financial%20services%20providers%2C%20and%20several%20others%20who%20provide%20follow-up%20care%20to%20patients%20outside%20of%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20Kaiser%20Permanente's%20responsibility%20to%20prevent%20this%20interruption%2C%20Dardon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20afford%20to%20have%20workers%20out%20on%20the%20picket%20line%20for%20two%20weeks%20and%20neglect%20patient%20care%2C%26quot%3B%20Dardon%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20part%20falls%20on%20Kaiser.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20interruptions%20to%20patient%20care%2C%20a%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20spokesperson%20directed%20Insider%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.kaiserpermanente.org%2Fwho-we-are%2Flabor-relations%2Falliance-bargaining-updates%2Faddressing-the-coalitions-threat-to-strike%5C%22%3EAugust%2024%20statement.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20take%20any%20threat%20to%20disrupt%20care%20for%20our%20members%20seriously%20and%20have%20plans%20to%20ensure%20continued%20access%20to%20healthcare%20by%20our%20members%2C%20patients%2C%20and%20the%20communities%20we%20serve%2C%20should%20any%20union%20call%20for%20a%20strike%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20reads.%20%26quot%3BOur%20members%2C%20patients%2C%20and%20our%20communities%20need%20us%20to%20be%20there%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20%26quot%3Bconfident%26quot%3B%20they%20will%20reach%20an%20agreement%20with%20workers%20ahead%20of%20their%20contract%20expiration%20on%20September%2030%2C%20according%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fabout.kaiserpermanente.org%2Fwho-we-are%2Flabor-relations%2Ffocused-on-being-an-employer-of-choice%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225973%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20sign%20of%20different%20offices%20and%20clinics%20in%20a%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20hospital%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f36e4c1b7ced0019c76a5d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHealthcare%20employees%20providing%20both%20hospital%20and%20out-patient%20care%20are%20members%20of%20the%20Coalition.%3Cp%3EMike%20Blake%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3EShort%20staffing%20prevents%20quality%20healthcare%2C%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20patients%20and%20workers%20say%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EShort-staffing%20is%20the%20No.%201%20issue%20impacting%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20employees%20and%20patients%20alike%2C%20causing%20patients%20to%20face%20long%20wait%20lists%20to%20see%20providers%2C%20said%20Miriam%20De%20La%20Paz%2C%20a%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20employee%20of%20almost%2020%20years%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20union%20organizer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20feel%20that%20it's%20OK%20that%20our%20patients%20have%20to%20wait%20two%2C%20three%20months%20for%20an%20appointment%20because%20there's%20not%20enough%20personnel%20to%20be%20able%20to%20open%20up%20more%20slots%20or%20more%20times%20to%20be%20seen%2C%26quot%3B%20De%20La%20Paz%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20scary%20for%20our%20patients.%20Say%20you%20were%20diagnosed%20with%20cancer%20%E2%80%94%20how%20long%20do%20you%20have%20to%20wait%20for%20that%20appointment%20before%20you're%20actually%20seen%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhospitals-staff-shortages-pandemic-burnout-2021-8%5C%22%3EStaffing%20shortages%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20posed%20a%20problem%20at%20healthcare%20facilities%20across%20the%20nation%20since%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20in%20large%20part%20because%20of%20severe%20burn-out%20among%20healthcare%20providers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20patients%20like%20Mark%20Mason%2C%20the%20impacts%20of%20staff%20shortages%20are%20all%20too%20real%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20says%20a%20strike%20could%20be%20a%20potential%20solution.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMason%20said%20his%20%26quot%3Bcomplete%20and%20unequivocal%26quot%3B%20support%20for%20the%20potential%20strike%20comes%20after%20years%20of%20frustration%20with%20the%20healthcare%20provider%20because%20of%20long%20wait%20times%20to%20see%20specialists.%20One%20provider%20even%20told%20Mason%20he'd%20need%20to%20wait%203%20to%209%20months%20for%20a%20procedure%20to%20address%20severe%20leg%20pain%2C%20according%20to%20correspondence%20Mason%20shared%20with%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20seems%20to%20me%20Kaiser%20has%20an%20unwritten%20policy%3A%20If%20your%20life%20is%20threatened%2C%20go%20to%20the%20ER.%20If%20not%2C%20get%20on%20a%20waiting%20list%2C%26quot%3B%20Mason%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKaiser%20Permanente%20says%20they%20hired%20more%20than%2029%2C000%20new%20employees%20last%20year%20and%20plan%20to%20exceed%20the%20number%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20their%20statement%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDardon%20said%20the%20union%20effort%20has%20received%20a%20significant%20amount%20of%20support%20from%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20patients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20members%20know%20that%20we've%20been%20voting%20all%20week%20here%20at%20different%20Kaiser%20sites%20in%20the%20Northwest%2C%26quot%3B%20Dardon%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20come%20to%20speak%20to%20us%20at%20our%20tents%2C%20bringing%20their%20concerns%20and%20listening%20to%20us.%20Their%20concerns%20are%20our%20concerns%20too%2C%20so%20we%20have%20the%20public%20support%20in%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKaiser%20needs%20to%20listen%20to%20that%20message%20from%20its%20workers%20and%20from%20its%20members%2C%26quot%3B%20Dardon%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20patient%20or%20employee%20impacted%20by%20staffing%20shortages%20or%20long%20wait%20times%3F%20Reach%20this%20reporter%20at%20khawkinson%40insider.com.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkaiser-permanente-worker-strike-union-patient-health-risk-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693821601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f36da07819260019108ba1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkaiser-permanente-worker-strike-union-patient-health-risk-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Patients%20agree%20with%20healthcare%20workers%20that%20Kaiser%20Permanente%20must%20address%20staffing%20shortages%20to%20protect%20patient%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22khawkinson%40insider.com%20(Katie%20Hawkinson%20)%2