EIn%202013-14%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20set%20up%20a%20non-lapsable%20corpus%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%20for%20special%20police%20helplines%2C%20safety%20in%20transportation%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202013-14%2C%20Rs%201%2C000%20crore%20was%20allocated%20for%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%20fund%2C%20which%20was%20then%20reduced%20to%20Rs%20550%20crore%20in%202017-18%2C%202018-19%2C%20and%202019-20.%20It%20was%20further%20reduced%20to%20around%20Rs%20500%20crore%20in%202021-22%20and%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20utilisation%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%20fund%20is%20also%20very%20poor.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2F164.100.77.118%2Fview_detail%2FeyJpdiI6IjFtY3I3cUdYbVVpMG1Lb2tpdnk5SkE9PSIsInZhbHVlIjoiNFZ1Wlp0Mmphb2xpVmpvckVxZk1mdz09IiwibWFjIjoiZTdmZjllYjQ2NmJiNGQyZjM3ZmY1YmIxY2ZiYWQwMWE5MTJlOTljYTI3ZDc1NGIwN2YyNDJjMTBmNmExOTJlNiJ9%5C%22%3EAs%20on%20April%2028%2C%202023%2C%20around%20Rs%2012%2C008.5%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20appraised%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Nirbhaya%E2%80%99%20project%2C%20of%20which%20only%20Rs%204%2C923%20crore%20has%20been%20released%20and%20Rs%202%2C521%20crore%20has%20been%20utilised%20(which%20is%20roughly%20around%2021%25%20of%20the%20appraised%20amount%20and%2051%25%20of%20the%20released%20amount).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20spent%20Rs%20160%20crore%20on%20another%20important%20scheme%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwcd.nic.in%2Fschemes%2Fone-stop-centre-scheme-1%5C%22%3EOne%20Stop%20Centre%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%2C%20in%202020-21.%20The%20scheme%2C%20initially%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98Mission%20for%20Protection%20and%20Empowerment%20for%20Women%E2%80%99%2C%20is%20now%20subsumed%2C%20with%20many%20other%20pre-existing%20and%20new%20schemes%2C%20under%20a%20new%20programme%2C%20%E2%80%98Sambal%E2%80%99%20of%20%E2%80%98Mission%20Shakti%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20no%20longer%20is%20possible%20to%20find%20out%20how%20much%20was%20allocated