2-year-old%20man%20has%20been%20arrested%20for%20allegedly%20abetting%20the%20suicide%20of%20his%20wife%20who%20jumped%20to%20death%20from%20the%20fourth%20floor%20of%20a%20building%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Thane%20district%2C%20police%20said%20on%20Monday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fmaharashtra-man-who-objected-to-wife-chatting-online-arrested-over-her-suicide-cops-4357508%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fmaharashtra-man-who-objected-to-wife-chatting-online-arrested-over-her-suicide-cops-4357508%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fcities%2Fmaharashtra-man-who-objected-to-wife-chatting-online-arrested-over-her-suicide-cops-4357508%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jharkand%20Government%20Hands%20Memo%20for%20Governor%20to%20Raj%20Bhawan%20Security%20After%20Failing%20to%20Get%20Appointment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04123209%2FF48K1wDXgAAyXu7.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20five-member%20delegation%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20government%E2%80%99s%20state%20coordination%20committee%20(SCC)%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Ehand%20over%20a%20memorandum%20for%20the%20governor%20to%20the%20security%20guard%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20his%20office%20after%20failing%20to%20secure%20an%20appointment%20with%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20urged%20governor%20C.P.%20Radhakrishnan%20to%20send%20observations%20on%20three%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20bills%E2%80%9D%20that%20had%20been%20returned%20by%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20emailed%20and%20also%20given%20a%20letter%20at%20Raj%20Bhavan%20on%20Friday%20%5BSeptember%201%5D%20seeking%20an%20appointment%20with%20the%20governor%20on%20Sunday%20%5BSeptember%203%5D.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20one%20available%20at%20the%20office%20and%20we%20had%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20memorandum%20at%20the%20gate%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20Vinod%20Pandey%2C%20an%20SSC%20member%20and%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20meet%20the%20governor%20and%20apprise%20him%20about%20the%20three%20important%20bills%20%E2%80%93%201932%20Khatiyan%20(land%20survey)%20based%20definition%20of%20locals%20bill%2C%20the%20anti-lynching%20bill%20and%20the%20bill%20pertaining%20to%20raising%20the%20reservation%20quota%20of%20OBC%20communities.%20All%20these%20bills%20had%20been%20returned%20by%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20without%20sending%20the%20necessary%20observations%20of%20the%20governor%20(both%20former%20governor%20Ramesh%20Bais%20and%20incumbent%20C.P.%20Radhakrishnan).%20We%20want%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20to%20send%20the%20observations%20so%20that%20the%20necessary%20corrections%20can%20be%20done%20and%20reintroduced%20in%20the%20Assembly%20and%20send%20it%20again%20to%20Raj%20Bhavan%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCC%20members%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F04%2Fjharkhand-ruling-alliance-members-submit-memo-to-governors-guard-on-3-bills-2611490.html%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20has%20not%20mentioned%20the%20specific%20objections%20in%20the%20Bills%2C%20violating%20Article%20200%20of%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SSC%20has%20been%20formed%20by%20the%20three%20ruling%20ally%20parties%20in%20Jharkhand%20%E2%80%93%20Congress%2C%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20and%20JMM.%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20Radhakrishnan%20is%20a%20former%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20MP%20and%20has%20also%20served%20as%20the%20BJP%20state%20president%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20accused%20the%20governor%20of%20working%20at%20the%20behest%20of%20%E2%80%9Ca%20particular%20party%20or%20person%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ENew%20Indian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%20(TNIE)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2Fsep%2F04%2Fjharkhand-ruling-alliance-members-submit-memo-to-governors-guard-on-3-bills-2611490.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20the%20governor%20does%20not%20want%20local%20and%20reservation%20policies%20to%20be%20formulated%2C%E2%80%9D%20Pandey%20was%20quoted%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3ETNIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%20They%20want%20the%20governor%20to%20clear%20his%20stand%20on%20the%20three%20bills%20passed%20by%20the%20state%20Assembly%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EState%20Congress%20chief%20Rajesh%20Thakur%20said%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20leaders%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%20are%20not%20given%20time%20by%20the%20Raj%20Bhawan.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20opposition%20leaders%20freely%20enter%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20house%20and%20set%20their%20agenda%2C%E2%80%9D%20Thakur%20was%20quoted%20by%20%3Cem%3ETNIE%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Bills%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%E2%80%99s%20secretariat%20had%20in%20July%20issued%20a%20communique%20detailing%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20intent%20to%20reintroduce%20the%20three%20bills%20and%20their%20request%20to%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20secretariat%20to%20forward%20the%20observations%20made%20by%20the%20governor%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBills%20passed%20by%20the%20Assembly%20are%20sent%20to%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20for%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20assent.%20The%20copy%20of%20the%20bills%20consists%20of%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20observations%20in%20case%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan%20consents%20to%20them%20or%20has%20some%20objections.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20case%20of%20these%20bills%2C%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20observations%20are%20missing.%20Since%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20re-introduce%20the%20bills%2C%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20observations%20have%20been%20sought%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20statement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Eread%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20Definition%20for%20Local%20Persons%20and%20for%20Extending%20Consequential%2C%20Social%2C%20Cultural%20and%20Other%20Benefits%20to%20Such%20Local%20Persons%20Bill%20of%202022%20set%20the%20land%20survey%20settlements%20of%201932%20as%20the%20benchmark%20for%20identifying%20the%20locals%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20bill%20was%20passed%20in%20an%20extended%20monsoon%20session%20last%20year%2C%20but%20returned%20by%20the%20then%20governor%20Ramesh%20Bais%20stating%20that%20it%20violated%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jharkhand%20(Prevention%20of%20Violence%20and%20Mob%20Lynching)%20Bill%20of%202021%2C%20passed%20in%20the%20winter%20session%20of%202021%2C%20was%20returned%20by%20Bais%20seeking%20clarity%20on%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%98mob%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20OBC%20reservation%20bill%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20increase%20reservations%20for%20OBC%20communities%20to%2027%25%20from%2014%25%20was%20returned%20by%20Radhakrishnan%20earlier%20this%20year%20after%20receiving%20the%20opinion%20of%20the%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20development%20holds%20significance%20as%20these%20issues%20have%20been%20at%20the%20core%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20government%E2%80%99s%20political%20narrative%20besides%20being%20electoral%20promises%20in%20the%202019%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fjharkhand%2Fjharkhand-governments-state-coordination-committee-hands-memorandum-for-governor-to-raj-bhavan%2Fcid%2F1963574%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693816248000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04123209%2FF48K1wDXgAAyXu7.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjharkand-government-hands-memo-for-governor-to-raj-bhawan-security-after-failing-to-get-appointment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20memorandum%20urged%20governor%20C.P.%20Radhakrishnan%20to%20send%20observations%20on%20three%20%E2%80%9Cimportant%20bills%E2%80%9D%20which%20had%20been%20returned%20by%20the%20Raj%20Bhavan.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fjharkand-government-hands-memo-for-governor-to-raj-bhawan-security-after-failing-to-get-appointment%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20a%20Record%20Dry%20August%2C%20Is%20India's%20Kharif%20Harvest%20in%20Trouble%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04102045%2F11835209326_7c1729bdf5_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20supposedly%20August%20in%20Delhi%2C%20but%20once%20I%20look%20at%20my%20chilli%20and%20basil%20plants%2C%20they%20tell%20a%20different%20story.%20These%20terrace%20plants%20are%20running%20away%20from%20the%20sun%20and%20not%20towards%20it.%20The%20fragrant%20basil%20leaves%20look%20parched%20each%20noon%2C%20reminding%20me%20of%20the%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%2C%20and%20India%2C%20are%20experiencing%20a%20drought-like%20August.%20The%20figures%20speak%20for%20themselves%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fdriest-and-warmest-august-in-india-s-history-raises-concerns-for-agriculture-and-water-reserves-11693504910272.html%5C%22%3EIndia%20reported%20its%20driest%20and%20hottest%20August%20since%201901%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Reports%20also%20suggest%20this%20may%20be%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.skymetweather.com%2Fcontent%2Fweather-news-and-analysis%2Fdelhi-likely-to-see-second-driest-august-ever%2F%5C%22%3Esecond-driest%20August%20Delhi%20has%20ever%20seen%3C%2Fa%3E%20(the%20driest%20was%20in%202022).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReports%20from%20the%20west%20and%20south%2C%20including%20southwest%20Rajasthan%2C%20Gujarat%20and%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20Maharashtra%20and%20Karnataka%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Findia%2Findia-faces-record-low-august-rains-threatening-summer-crops-2023-08-18%2F%5C%22%3Eare%20not%20good%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20of%20these%20areas%20have%20received%20below%20average%20rainfall.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20El%20Ni%C3%B1o%20year%20and%20was%20expecting%20disruption%20in%20monsoons%20which%20may%20lead%20to%20droughts%20and%20food%20security%20problems.%20The%20predictions%20seem%20to%20be%20coming%20true%20as%20August%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outlookindia.com%2Fnational%2Fdriest-august-since-1901-recorded-by-india-meteorological-department-news-314924%5C%22%3E36%25%20below%20normal%20rainfall%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20southern%20peninsula%20reported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Findia%2Fdriest-august-for-southern-peninsula-since-1901-2668486%5C%22%3E60%25%20below%20average%20rainfall%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20alarming%20rain-fed%20farmers%20in%20these%20areas.%20These%20fears%20have%20also%20started%20to%20ring%20in%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20ears%2C%20as%20there%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Fmgnregs-work-demand-up-20-on-year-in-august-2023-shows-data-123090101150_1.html%5C%22%3E20%25%20increase%20demand%20for%20work%20under%20the%20MGNREGA%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0due%20to%20the%20vagaries%20of%20the%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20already%20gauging%20the%20situation%20have%20decreased%20paddy%20acreage%20by%20384%20hectares%2C%20a%204%25%20drop%20from%20the%20previous%20five-year%20average.%20Farmers%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20food%20bowl%20Punjab%2C%20Haryana%20and%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20in%20the%20north%20are%20also%20suffering%20the%20brunt%20of%20untimely%20rainfall.%20From%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20to%20Punjab%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20rainfall%20and%20floods%20have%20battered%20farmers%20and%20others.%20Other%20crops%20like%20legumes%2C%20oilseeds%20and%20paddy%20are%20affected%20by%20changing%20weather%20patterns.%20In%20retrospect%2C%20Cyclone%20Biparjoy%20heralded%20the%20monsoon%20deficit%20for%20the%20subcontinent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IMD%20may%20have%20predicted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fscience%2Fmint-explainer-understanding-imds-september-rainfall-projection-11693549982052.html%5C%22%3Enormal%20rainfall%20for%20September%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhy-the-ban-on-rice-exports-was-not-unexpected%5C%22%3Eaggressive%20ban%20on%20rice%20exports%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20custom%20duties%20on%20vegetables%20and%20other%20food%20products%20clear%20point%20to%20another%20reality.%20Our%20policy%20makers%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20imminent%20food%20crisis.%20If%20its%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20rain%20as%20expected%20in%20September%2C%20the%20rain-fed%20areas%20will%20undergo%20deep%20hardship%2C%20increasing%20pressure%20on%20the%20government.%20The%20people%20with%20irrigation%20options%20or%20%E2%80%9Cunderground%20boring%E2%80%9D%20will%20be%20heavily%20dependent%20on%20the%20ever-shrinking%20surface%20and%20ground%20water%20resources.%20Because%20there%20is%20no%20way%20the%20farmers%20or%20the%20government%20can%20afford%20another%20below%20average%20harvest.%20The%20Rabi%20harvests%20have%20been%20below%20average%20for%20the%20past%20two%20years%20now.%20Kharif%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20been%20the%20best%20either.%20Untimely%20rainfall%2C%20heatwaves%20and%20hailstorms%20have%20done%20the%20most%20damage%20across%20the%20subcontinent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20food%20stocks%20have%20already%20depleted%20and%20many%20police%20makers%20and%20farmers%20were%20hoping%20for%20a%20good%20harvest%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20nature%20has%20other%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgro-climatic%20crisis%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20time%20to%20zoom%20out%20a%20bit%2C%20and%20ask%20certain%20questions%3A%20What%20has%20been%20happening%20to%20India%3F%20Are%20things%20really%20changing%20agriculturally%3F%20Are%20we%20headed%20into%20a%20food%20crisis%3F%20The%20short%20answer%20to%20the%20last%20two%20questions%2C%20from%20everything%20we%20know%20so%20far%2C%20is%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20agro-climate%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20prolonged%20climate%20agrarian%20disruptions%20%E2%80%93%20became%20visible%20in%202019%2C%20with%20disrupted%20monsoons%2C%20floods%20and%20eight%20tropical%20cyclones.%20As%20per%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-seventh-most-affected-by-climate-change-in-2019-globally-report-101611552192319.html%5C%22%3Eglobal%20report%20on%20climate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20the%20seventh%20most-affected%20by%20the%20devastating%20impact%20of%20climate%20change%20globally%20in%202019%2C%E2%80%9D%20with%20changing%20climate%20eating%20as%20much%20as%200.72%25%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdding%20to%20the%20wound%20was%20the%20unusual%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Flocust-attack-india-jaipur-climate-change%5C%22%3E2020%20locust%20attack%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20reportedly%20the%20biggest%20such%20attack%20in%20over%20three%20decades.%20Locusts%20damaged%20crops%20all%20across%20the%20western%20and%20northern%20subcontinent.%20The%20untimely%20rainfall%20provided%20new%20breeding%20grounds%20for%20locusts%20in%20western%20India.%20This%20was%20another%20symptom%20of%20the%20agro-climate%20crisis%20building%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Is%20Indian%20Agriculture%20Following%20Two%20Policies%20%E2%80%93%20One%20at%20WTO%20and%20Another%20at%20Home%3F%C2%A0%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fmodi-agriculture-wto-msp-policies-niti-aayog%5C%22%3EIs%20Indian%20Agriculture%20Following%20Two%20Policies%20%E2%80%93%20One%20at%20WTO%20and%20Another%20at%20Home%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2021%20again%20showed%20untimely%20rainfalls%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpib.gov.in%2FPressreleaseshare.aspx%3FPRID%3D1696515%5C%22%3EIMD%20pointed%20out%20six%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%20receiving%20decreased%20rainfall%2C%20while%2012%20states%20had%20excessive%20rainfall.%20Overall%2C%20about%2040%25%20of%20the%20703%20districts%20in%20India%20had%20average%20rainfall.%20In%20six%20years%20(2015-21)%2C%20India%20lost%2033.9%20million%20hectares%20of%20crop%20land%20to%20floods%20and%20excess%20rains%20and%2035%20million%20hectares%20to%20drought%20%E2%80%93%20numbers%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20increase%20as%20years%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202022%2C%20we%20see%20the%20pattern%20re-emerging%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fheatwave-impact-wheat-yield-falls-by-13-5-in-punjab-101652211100645.html%5C%22%3Edampened%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rabi%20harvests%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.financialexpress.com%2Fpolicy%2Feconomy-heavy-rains-hit-kharif-crops-ahead-of-harvest-2706312%2F%5C%22%3Euntimely%3C%2Fa%3E%20kharif%20rains%20and%20kharif%20paddy%20production%20dropping%20by%206%25.%20Meanwhile%2C%20heat-related%20deaths%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1035871%2Fheat-related-deaths-in-india-increased-by-55-in-last-17-years-finds-lancet-study%5C%22%3Eincreased%20by%2055%25%20in%2017%20years%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20victims%20were%20not%20just%20humans%2C%20but%20also%20the%20Rabi%20wheat%20crop%20in%20north%20India%2C%20which%20reportedly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fchandigarh-news%2Fheatwave-impact-wheat-yield-falls-by-13-5-in-punjab-101652211100645.html%5C%22%3Eshrank%20by%20at%20least%2013.5%25%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20government%20was%20quick%20to%20ban%20wheat%20exports%2C%20while%20trying%20to%20curtail%20public%20panic.%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20in%20her%20parliament%20address%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fagriculture-sector-needs-re-orientation-due-to-likely-hurdles-in-climate-change-surge-in-costs-of-inputs-8416255%2F%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20(agriculture)%20grew%20by%203.0%25%20in%202021-22%20compared%20to%203.3%25%20in%202020-21%E2%80%9D%20and%20blamed%20the%20changing%20climate%20for%20it.%20She%20plainly%20also%20spelt%20out%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20%E2%80%9Cre-orient%E2%80%9D%20its%20policy%20to%20tackle%20the%20challenge%20of%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20a%20Punjab%20Agriculture%20University%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fpunjab-likely-to-suffer-yield-loss-of-all-major-crops-by-2050-due-to-temp-rise-climate-study%2Farticleshow%2F97259650.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20concurs%20with%20the%20finance%20minister%E2%80%99s%20view%20and%20predicts%20that%20Punjab%20by%202050%20will%20be%20grappling%20with%20changing%20climate%20and%20experience%20significant%20yield%20loss%20due%20to%20rising%20temperatures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202022-23%20Rabi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fkharif-rice-production-to-drop-by-6-agriculture-ministry-8165444%2F%5C%22%3Ewas%20no%20different%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Different%20parts%20of%20India%20experience%20climatic%20issues%2C%20mainly%20untimely%20rainfall.%20Punjab%20and%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20were%20affected.%20And%20then%20came%20Biparjoy%2C%20tearing%20into%20the%20western%20subcontinent%20and%20drying%20up%20our%20monsoons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20the%20second%2C%20economic%20phase%20of%20the%20agro-climatic%20crisis%20is%20reached%20%E2%80%93%20hyper%20food%20inflation.%20From%20tomatoes%20and%20onions%2C%20now%20the%20inflation%20is%20reaching%20other%20staples%20like%20legumes%20and%20vegetables.%20Fodder%20prices%20are%20increasing%20gradually%2C%20as%20the%20Indian%20system%20is%20losing%20its%20resilience%20because%20of%20climate%20disruptions.%20A%20majority%20of%20government%20schemes%20have%20failed%20to%20build%20infrastructure%20or%20freight%20networks%20for%20storage%20and%20preventing%20climate-related%20harvest%20damages.%20From%20hailstorms%20in%20Kashmir%20to%20a%20dry%20August%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20farmers%20are%20least%20prepared%2C%20and%20hence%20harvest%20losses%20will%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeep%20in%20mind%20that%20our%20strategic%20food%20reserves%20are%20at%20their%20lowest%2C%20and%20800%20million%20are%20directly%20fed%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20public%20distribution%20system.%20With%20the%20rupee%20floating%20around%2082-83%20to%20the%20dollar%20and%20the%20Ukraine-Russia%20conflict%20still%20escalating%2C%20we%20can%E2%80%99t%20really%20depend%20on%20the%20international%20market%20for%20our%20food%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20third%20stage%20of%20the%20agro-climate%20food%20crisis%20%E2%80%93%20the%20convergence%20phase.%20If%20the%20kharif%20harvest%20fails%20or%20is%20again%20below%20average%2C%20Indian%20food%20security%20will%20be%20deeply%20impacted%20due%20to%20the%20compounding%20of%20climate-related%20agrarian%20losses.%20We%20will%20be%20in%20the%20third%20stage%20of%20the%20crisis%20once%20the%20agriculture%20production%20is%20hampered%20and%20the%20economic%20measures%20fail%20to%20control%20hyper-food%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20or%20three%20cycles%20of%20this%20pattern%2C%20and%20any%20country%20is%20looking%20straight%20at%20a%20full%20blown%20agro-climate%20crisis.%20Bad%20harvests%2C%20repeated%20climate%20disruptions%2C%20hyper-food%20inflation%2C%20scarcity%20and%20no%20international%20supplies%20together%20are%20a%20malnutrition%20time%20bomb.%20If%20our%20agrarian%20trajectory%20is%20not%20changed%2C%202024%20or%202025%20maybe%20the%20years%20where%20a%20full%20nutritious%20meal%20is%20a%20privilege%20few%20can%20afford.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndra%20Shekhar%20Singh%20is%20an%20independent%20agri-policy%20analyst%20and%20writer.%20He%20was%20the%20former%20director%2C%20policy%20and%20outreach%2C%20NSAI.%20He%20also%20hosts%20The%20Wire%20agri-talk%20show%20%E2%80%98Krishi%20ki%20baat%2FFarm%20Talks%E2%80%99.%20He%20tweets%20on%20%40indrassingh.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693816231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04102045%2F11835209326_7c1729bdf5_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fafter-a-record-dry-august-is-indias-kharif-harvest-in-trouble%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20IMD%20may%20have%20predicted%20normal%20rainfall%20for%20September%2C%20but%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20aggressive%20ban%20on%20rice%20exports%20and%20other%20custom%20duties%20on%20vegetables%20and%20other