%20received%20an%20invitation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-go-even-if-im-invited-uma-bharti-on-no-call-for-big-bjp-march-4357346%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-go-even-if-im-invited-uma-bharti-on-no-call-for-big-bjp-march-4357346%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwont-go-even-if-im-invited-uma-bharti-on-no-call-for-big-bjp-march-4357346%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22G20%20Summit%20FAQs%3A%20Will%20Morning%20Walks%20Be%20Allowed%3F%20Are%20Theatres%20Open%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20G20%20Summit%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Delhi%20this%20weekend.%20It%20will%20see%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20gatherings%20of%20world%20leaders%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20for%20two%20days.%20These%20include%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20Canada%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%2C%20UK's%20Rishi%20Sunak%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20King%20Salman%20bin%20Abdulaziz%20Saud%20along%20with%20several%20other%20heads%20of%20state.%20Considering%20the%20high-profile%20nature%20of%20the%20event%2C%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20made%20elaborate%20security%20arrangements%20and%20created%20regulatory%20zones%20in%20coordination%20with%20the%20traffic%20police%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20flow%20of%20traffic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Fg20-summit-new-delhi-travelling-during-g20-heres-how-you-can-reach-railway-stations-airport-4357021%5C%22%3ETravelling%20During%20G20%3F%20Here's%20How%20You%20Can%20Reach%20Railway%20Stations%2C%20Airport%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20curbs%20and%20regulations%20will%20cover%20the%20New%20Delhi%20district%2C%20and%20come%20into%20effect%20from%20the%20night%20of%20September%207%2C%20days%20before%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D