2%2C%22engagement%22%3A310%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66702893%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66702893.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66702893.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Modi%20Govt%20Minister%2C%20Kaushal%20Kishore%2C%20Again%20Finds%20Himself%20Linked%20to%20a%20Crime%20Story%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04084624%2F202675217_4109853105797268_6156076208974483869_n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20would%20have%20been%20a%20routine%20crime%20story%20had%20it%20not%20involved%20a%20murder%20weapon%20and%20crime%20scene%20linked%20to%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20Narendra%20Modi-led%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20night%20of%20August%2031%2C%20six%20men%20gathered%20in%20a%20house%20in%20the%20Thakurganj%20area%20of%20Lucknow%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20to%20party.%20They%20got%20drunk%20and%20played%20cards%20till%20late.%20At%20around%202%20am%2C%20they%20ate%20dinner%2C%20following%20which%20two%20of%20those%20present%20went%20home%20to%20sleep.%20The%20remaining%20four%20continued%20to%20drink%20and%20gamble%20till%204%20am.%20Things%20turned%20sour%20when%20one%20of%20them%2C%20Vinay%20Srivastava%2C%20accused%20the%20other%20three%20of%20ganging%20up%20against%20him.%20He%20had%20lost%20Rs%2012%2C000%20in%20bets%20and%20was%20irked%20that%20the%20other%20three%20were%20ending%20the%20game%20to%20prevent%20him%20from%20recovering%20his%20losses.%20The%20disagreement%20soon%20turned%20physical.%20Blows%20were%20exchanged.%20Vinay%E2%80%99s%20shirt%20was%20completely%20torn.%20Then%2C%20one%20of%20the%20other%20three%20men%20grabbed%20a%20revolver%20that%20was%20kept%20under%20a%20pillow%20on%20the%20bed%20in%20one%20of%20the%20rooms%20and%20shot%20Vinay%20in%20the%20head.%20He%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%20Police%20arrested%20the%20three%20men%2C%20Ajay%20Rawat%20(32)%2C%20Ankit%20Verma%20(27)%20and%20Shamim%20(21)%20and%20claimed%20the%20three%20had%20confessed%20to%20the%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20joint%20commissioner%20of%20police%20(HQ%20and%20crime)%20Akash%20Kulhary%20found%20in%20the%20preliminary%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20licensed%20revolver%20used%20in%20the%20crime%20belonged%20to%20Vikas%20Kishore%20aka%20Ashu%2C%20the%20son%20of%20BJP%20MP%20from%20Mohanlalganj%20and%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20housing%20and%20urban%20affairs%2C%20Kaushal%20Kishore.%20The%20incident%20happened%20in%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s%20house.%20Kishore%20said%20his%20son%20was%20in%20Delhi%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crime.%20On%20September%202%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Lucknow%20police%20lodged%20an%20FIR%20against%20Vikas%20under%20Section%2030%20of%20the%20Arms%20Act%20and%20started%20the%20process%20to%20cancel%20the%20weapon%E2%80%99s%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVikas%2C%2028%2C%20is%20the%20vice-president%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Dalit%20morcha%20in%20UP%E2%80%99s%20Awadh%20region.%20His%20father%20Kaushal%20Kishore%20is%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20state%20president%20of%20the%20SC%2FST%20wing.%20The%20victim%2C%20Vinay%2C%20was%20Vikas%E2%80%99s%20close%20associate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22The%20Past%20and%20Future%20of%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20%E2%80%93%20And%20Why%20Both%20are%20Attractive%20to%20the%20BJP%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Famarmani-tripathi-uttar-pradesh-adityanath-bjp%5C%22%3EThe%20Past%20and%20Future%20of%20Amarmani%20Tripathi%20%E2%80%93%20And%20Why%20Both%20are%20Attractive%20to%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20murder%20may%20have%20been%20solved%20but%20the%20scandal%20has%20left%20another%20stain%20on%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20image.%20His%20fascinating%20political%20journey%20%E2%80%93%20from%20being%20a%20grounded%20Dalit%20Communist%20leader%20to%20ending%20up%20as%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20saffron%20camp%20%E2%80%93%20marking%20the%20shifts%20in%20caste%20mobilisation%20in%20the%20state%2C%20is%20a%20story%20of%20its%20own.%20However%2C%20in%20the%20last%20three-four%20years%2C%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20public%20image%20as%20a%20leader%20with%20a%20clean%20record%20has%20been%20overshadowed%20by%20the%20controversies%20surrounding%20three%20of%20his%20four%20sons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incidents%20range%20from%20plain%20embarrassment%20caused%20by%20one%20son%20for%20staging%20a%20murder%20attempt%20on%20himself%20to%20the%20tragedy%20of%20losing%20another%20to%20alcohol%20abuse%2C%20and%20now%20this%20murder%20case%20in%20Lucknow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20October%202020%2C%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20son%20Aakash%20Kishore%20died%20due%20to%20liver%20cirrhosis%20after%20years%20of%20alcohol%20abuse.%20Shattered%20by%20the%20loss%2C%20Kishore%20vowed%20to%20end%20alcoholism%20and%20rolled%20out%20a%20social%20campaign%20against%20alcohol%20and%20other%20substance%20abuse%20%E2%80%93%20Nashamukti%20Samaj%20Andolan%20or%20Campaign%20for%20a%20Drug%20Free%20Society.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20organised%20numerous%20awareness%20meetings%2C%20half-marathons%2C%20social%20media%20live%20events%20and%20pledge%20ceremonies%20against%20use%20of%20drugs.%20Kishore%20even%20asks%20people%20in%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20Mohanlalganj%2C%20which%20circles%20Lucknow%2C%20to%20take%20a%20pledge%20against%20drugs%20and%20alcohol%20on%20festivals%20such%20as%20Holi.%20He%20appeals%20to%20people%20to%20not%20get%20their%20daughters%20married%20to%20men%20who%20drink%20alcohol%20or%20use%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20ensure%20that%20no%20other%20person%20loses%20his%20son%20to%20nasha%2C%20I%20will%20work%20till%20my%20last%20breath%20to%20save%20children%20and%20the%20youth%20from%20nasha%20and%20make%20India%20nashamukt%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20minister%20said%20recently.%20On%20International%20Youth%20Day%2C%20this%20August%2C%20chief%20minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20launched%20a%20state-wide%20campaign%20against%20drugs%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%98Nasha%20Mukt%20Pradesh%2C%20Shashakt%20Pradesh%20Abhiyan%E2%80%99.%20At%20the%20event%2C%20Adityanath%20referred%20to%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20son%20Aakash%20as%20an%20example%20to%20warn%20the%20youth%20against%20the%20ills%20of%20drug%20abuse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kishore%20is%20using%20his%20son%20Aakash%E2%80%99s%20tragic%20demise%20to%20promote%20anti-alcoholism%2C%20his%20second%20son%20Ayush%20has%20brought%20him%20all%20the%20negative%20headlines%20due%20to%20controversies%20in%20his%20personal%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202021%2C%20Ayush%20was%20shot%20by%20someone%20in%20Lucknow.%20This%20raised%20questions%20on%20the%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Kishore%20was%20left%20embarrassed%20after%20police%20revealed%20a%20few%20hours%20later%20that%20Ayush%20had%20staged%20an%20attack%20on%20himself.%20Ayush%20got%20himself%20shot%20by%20his%20brother-in-law%20Adarsh%20to%20frame%20someone%20else%20in%20the%20case%2C%20police%20said%2C%20booking%20the%20two%20in%20an%20FIR.%20Adarsh%20was%20later%20arrested.%20Police%20said%20they%20cracked%20the%20case%20after%20they%20found%20Adarsh%E2%80%99s%20activity%20to%20be%20suspicious%20and%20recovered%20a%20pistol%20used%20in%20the%20firing%20from%20the%20house%20where%20the%20MP%E2%80%99s%20son%20was%20staying.%20Two%20shots%20were%20fired.%20The%20first%20one%20hit%20a%20wall.%20The%20second%20touched%20Ayush%20and%20went%20past%20him.%20But%20the%20drama%20didn%E2%80%99t%20end%20there.%20Ayush%20had%20entered%20into%20an%20inter-caste%20love%20marriage%20with%20a%20woman%20his%20family%20did%20not%20approve%20of.%20He%20had%20been%20living%20separately%20from%20his%20father.%20Kishore%20had%20to%20come%20out%20in%20public%20and%20explain%20why%20the%20family%20disapproved%20of%20her%2C%20in%20unnecessary%20drama%20from%20his%20point%20of%20view.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Gladstone%20Scion%20to%20Apologise%20for%20Slavery%3A%20Can%20Indian%20Upper%20Castes%20Too%20Look%20Within%3F%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fgladstone-scion-apologise-slavery-indian-upper-castes-look-within%5C%22%3EGladstone%20Scion%20to%20Apologise%20for%20Slavery%3A%20Can%20Indian%20Upper%20Castes%20Too%20Look%20Within%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20after%20the%20staged%20shooting%2C%20Kishore%E2%80%99s%20estranged%20daughter-in-law%20Ankita%20Singh%20reached%20outside%20the%20MP%E2%80%99s%20residence%20and%20slit%20her%20wrists.%20She%20had%20to%20be%20hospitalised.%20In%20a%20video%20before%20attempting%20suicide%2C%20she%20accused%20the%20MP%2C%20his%20wife%20Jai%20Devi%20(a%20BJP%20MLA)%20and%20her%20husband%20Ayush%20of%20mistreating%20her%20and%20intimidating%20her.%20Kishore%20was%20again%20drawn%20to%20public%20scrutiny%20as%20the%20drama%20played%20out%20on%20television%20channels.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20is%20doing%20all%20this%20to%20tarnish%20our%20image%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kishore%20said%20then%2C%20refusing%20to%20acknowledge%20Ankita%20as%20his%20daughter-in-law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishore%20was%20born%20in%20rural%20Lucknow%20in%20a%20Dalit%20family%2C%20one%20not%20in%20public%20life%2C%20in%201960.%20His%20father%20went%20around%20villages%20selling%20vegetables%20on%20a%20cycle.%20After%20being%20active%20in%20Left%20politics%20during%20his%20student%20days%2C%20Kishore%20took%20the%20plunge%20into%20electoral%20politics%20at%20the%20age%20of%2025.%20In%201985%2C%20he%20contested%20his%20first%20assembly%20election%20from%20Malihabad%20constituency%20as%20a%20candidate%20of%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India.%20Malihabad%20is%20a%20town%20known%20world%20over%20for%20its%20variety%20of%20delicious%20mangoes.%20But%20for%20Kishore%2C%20his%20political%20debut%20was%20not%20so%20sweet.%20He%20lost.%20The%20same%20result%20followed%20when%20he%20contested%20again%20in%201993%20and%201996.%20But%20his%20position%20improved%20vastly.%20He%20stood%20second%20to%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%E2%80%99s%20candidate%20Gauri%20Shankar%20on%20both%20occasions%2C%20losing%20by%20less%20than%207%2C000%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202002%2C%20when%20the%20CPI%20got%20into%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20SP%2C%20Kishore%20parted%20ways%20with%20the%20party%20as%20his%20seat%20went%20to%20Mulayam%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20party%2C%20and%20contested%20as%20an%20independent.%20He%20finally%20cracked%20the%20code%20and%20defeated%20Gauri%20Shankar%20by%20more%20than%2025%2C000%20votes.%20For%20his%20support%20to%20the%20Mulayam%20Singh%20government%2C%20he%20was%20rewarded%20with%20a%20ministerial%20berth%20and%20served%20as%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20labour.%20Kishore%20then%20went%20on%20to%20form%20his%20own%20party%20%E2%80%93%20Rashtrawadi%20Communist%20Party%20%E2%80%93%20and%20contested%20two%20assembly%20elections%20on%20its%20symbol%20in%202007%20and%202012.%20However%2C%20he%20lost%20by%20thin%20margins%20on%20both%20occasions.%20Earlier%20in%202004%2C%20he%20even%20contested%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20as%20an%20RCP%20candidate%20but%20lost%20even%20though%20he%20secured%20a%20decent%20tally%20of%2025%2C000%20votes%20on%20his%20own%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuccessive%20defeats%20had%20come%20as%20a%20huge%20setback.%20And%20after%20the%202012%20defeat%2C%20he%20had%20to%20struggle%20a%20lot.%20But%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20up.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20only%20three%20to%20four%20people%20would%20turn%20up%20at%20a%20meeting%20but%20he%20would%20still%20conduct%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20former%20close%20aide%20of%20the%20minister%E2%80%99s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20when%20Kishore%20decided%20he%20needed%20the%20support%20of%20a%20mainstream%20party.%20In%202014%2C%20months%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20BJP.%20The%20decision%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20fruitful.%20Riding%20on%20the%20popularity%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20resources%2C%20Kishore%20was%20elected%20the%20MP%20from%20Mohanlalganj.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20the%20president%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20UP%20Dalit%20wing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20clout%20grew%2C%20in%202017%2C%20he%20ensured%20his%20wife%20Jai%20Devi%20got%20a%20ticket%20from%20Malihabad.%20She%20was%20elected%20as%20a%20BJP%20MLA.%20In%202018%2C%20as%20the%20BJP%20prepared%20to%20expand%20its%20vote%20bank%20anticipating%20a%20joint%20opposition%20in%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Kishore%20oversaw%20meetings%20where%20the%20party%20reached%20out%20to%20various%20Dalit%20castes%20individually%20and%20spoke%20to%20them%20about%20the%20welfare%20schemes%20of%20the%20government%20benefitting%20them.%20Kaushal%20was%20elected%20an%20MP%20for%20a%20second%20time%20in%202019.%20Jai%20Devi%20too%20won%20her%20seat%20again%20in%20the%202022%20assembly%20elections%2C%20though%20with%20a%20reduced%20margin%20of%207%2C745%20votes.%20Her%20brother%20Amrish%20Kumar%20was%20also%20elected%20as%20a%20BJP%20MLA%20from%20Mohanlalganj%20assembly%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20July%202021%2C%20in%20a%20message%20to%20the%20Pasi%20community%20in%20UP%2C%20Kishore%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%20Union%20council%20of%20ministers%20ahead%20of%20the%202022%20state%20assembly%20elections.%20Kaushal%20is%20largely%20seen%20as%20the%20Pasi%20face%20of%20the%20BJP%20today.%20The%20Pasis%20are%20the%20second%20largest%20Dalit%20community%20in%20UP%20after%20Jatavs%20and%20are%20numerically%20concentrated%20in%20districts%20in%20Awadh%20and%20Purvanchal.%20Since%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20single%20leader%20or%20party%20loyalty%2C%20their%20votes%20are%20always%20up%20for%20grabs.%20There%20are%20several%20constituencies%20in%20central%20UP%20where%20a%20candidate%20cannot%20win%20without%20the%20support%20of%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Adityanath%E2%80%99s%20second%20term%2C%20Kishore%20has%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20appropriate%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20under%20the%20banner%20of%20Parakh%20Mahasangh%2C%20an%20outfit%20he%20started%20for%20oppressed%20and%20deprived%20sections%2C%20he%20held%20a%20seminar%20on%20%E2%80%98The%20Role%20of%20BJP%20and%20RSS%20in%20taking%20forward%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20mission%E2%80%99.%20This%20year%20too%2C%20he%20conducted%20a%20similar%20event%20on%20Ambedkar%20Jayanti%20in%20Lucknow.%20The%20theme%20was%20%E2%80%98BJP%20government%20and%20RSS%20are%20fulfilling%20Dr.%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20mission%20of%20a%20society%20free%20of%20caste%20and%20oppression%E2%80%99.%20The%20publicity%20material%20distributed%20for%20the%20event%20had%20Ambedkar%20on%20one%20flank%2C%20and%20Sangh%20ideologues%20Keshav%20Baliram%20Hedgewar%20and%20Syama%20Prasad%20Mukherjee%20on%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKishore%E2%80%99s%20former%20aide%20said%20that%20him%20%E2%80%9Cgoing%20astray%20ideologically%E2%80%9D%20was%20a%20reason%20why%20many%20of%20his%20old-time%2C%20core%20supporters%2C%20including%20himself%2C%20were%20leaving%20him%20and%20joining%20the%20SP.%20In%202021%2C%20one%20of%20Kaushal%E2%80%99s%20daughters-in-law%20lost%20her%20election%20for%20the%20zila%20panchayat.%20HIs%20supporters%20say%20that%20despite%20controversies%20surrounding%20his%20family%2C%20Kishore%20is%20still%20a%20popular%20leader%2C%20considered%20accessible%20by%20all%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693805459000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F04084624%2F202675217_4109853105797268_6156076208974483869_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fp