ndia.com%2F%3Fp%3D328846%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sibi%20Manivannan%20runs%20Gramiyaa%2C%20a%20spin%20on%20his%20grandfather%E2%80%99s%20old%20village%20shop%2C%20which%20sells%20wood%20cold-pressed%20oils%20across%20the%20world%20to%20reintroduce%20them%20in%20Indian%20kitchens.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F328846%2Fsibi-manivannan-runs-gramiya-cold-pressed-oils-earns-crores%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Punjab%20Farmer%20Gave%20Up%20Wheat%20Farming%20to%20Grow%20Exotic%20Flowers%2C%20Earns%20Rs%201%20Lakh%2FAcre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EGurwinder%20Singh%20Sohi%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20around%20wheat%20fields%20in%20Punjab%2C%20decided%20in%202008%20to%20harness%20the%20region%E2%80%99s%20favourable%20climate%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20the%20farmers%20by%20switching%20from%20wheat%20farming%20to%20floriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20generations%2C%20my%20family%20has%20cultivated%20wheat%20and%20rice.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20that%20despite%20the%20hard%20work%20farmers%20put%20into%20their%20fields%20day%20and%20night%2C%20they%20struggle%20to%20earn%20a%20decent%20income%20from%20it.%20In%20contrast%2C%20floriculture%20can%20yield%20two%20to%20three%20times%20the%20income%20compared%20to%20traditional%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303472%2Fjagmohan-singh-nagi-punjab-starts-kulwant-nutrition-corn-business-farming%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewheat%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2045-year-old%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBesides%2C%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20climate%20is%20ideal%20for%20growing%20most%20crops.%20The%20sandy%20loam%20soil%20and%20water%20with%20a%20pH%20of%207%E2%80%937.5%20are%20beneficial%20for%20flower%20cultivation.%20That%E2%80%99s